quran[665]{c,v,t}:
  10,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABIL-HEKIMI
  10,2,‘EKANE LILNNASI ‘AXHEBÆN ‘EN ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA REXHULIN MINHUM ‘EN ‘ENDHIRI EN-NASE WE BESHSHIRIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘ENNE LEHUM KADEME SIDKIN ‘INDE RABBIHIM KALEL-KAFIRUNE ‘INNE HADHA LESAHIRUN MUBINUN
  10,3,‘INNE REBBEKUMU ELLAHUL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE FI SITTETI ‘EJJAMIN THUMME ESTEWA ‘ALEL-’ARSHI JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE MA MIN SHEFI’IN ‘ILLA MIN BA’DI ‘IDHNIHI DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM FA’BUDUHU ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  10,4,‘ILEJHI MERXHI’UKUM XHEMI’ÆN WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKÆN ‘INNEHU JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU LIJEXHZIJEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI BIL-KISTI WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEHUM SHERABUN MIN HEMIMIN WE ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN BIMA KANU JEKFURUNE
  10,5,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE ESH-SHEMSE DIJA’EN WEL-KAMERE NURÆN WE KADDEREHU MENAZILE LITA’LEMU ‘ADEDE ES-SININE WEL-HISABE MA HALEKAL-LAHU DHALIKE ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI JUFESSILUL-’AJATI LIKAWMIN JA’LEMUNE
  10,6,‘INNE FI EHTILAFIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI WE MA HALEKAL-LAHU FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JETTEKUNE
  10,7,‘INNEL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA WE REDU BIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE ETME’ENNU BIHA WEL-LEDHINE HUM ‘AN ‘AJATINA GAFILUNE
  10,8,‘ULA’IKE ME’WAHUMU EN-NARU BIMA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  10,9,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI JEHDIHIM REBBUHUM BI’IMANIHIM TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHIMUL-’ENHARU FI XHENNATI EN-NA’IMI
  10,10,DA’WAHUM FIHA SUBHANEKEL-LEHUMME WE TEHIJETUHUM FIHA SELAMUN WE ‘AHIRU DA’WAHUM ‘ENIL-HEMDU LILLAHI RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  10,11,WE LEW JU’AXHXHILU ELLAHU LILNNASI ESH-SHERRE ESTI’XHALEHUM BIL-HAJRI LEKUDIJE ‘ILEJHIM ‘EXHELUHUM FENEDHERUL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA FI TUGJANIHIM JA’MEHUNE
  10,12,WE ‘IDHA MESSEL-’INSANE ED-DURRU DA’ANA LIXHENBIHI ‘EW KA’IDÆN ‘EW KA’IMÆN FELEMMA KESHEFNA ‘ANHU DURREHU MERRE KE’EN LEM JED’UNA ‘ILA DURRIN MESSEHU KEDHALIKE ZUJJINE LILMUSRIFINE MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  10,13,WE LEKAD ‘EHLEKNAL-KURUNE MIN KABLIKUM LEMMA DHELEMU WE XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI WE MA KANU LIJU’UMINU KEDHALIKE NEXHZIL-KAWMEL-MUXHRIMINE
  10,14,THUMME XHE’ALNAKUM HALA’IFE FIL-’ERDI MIN BA’DIHIM LINENDHURE KEJFE TA’MELUNE
  10,15,WE ‘IDHA TUTLA ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATUNA BEJJINATIN KALEL-LEDHINE LA JERXHUNE LIKA’ENA E’TI BIKUR’ANIN GAJRI HADHA ‘EW BEDDILHU KUL MA JEKUNU LI ‘EN ‘UBEDDILEHU MIN TILKA’I NEFSI ‘IN ‘ETTEBI’U ‘ILLA MA JUHA ‘ILEJJE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘IN ‘ASEJTU RABBI ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘A
  10,16,KUL LEW SHA’EL-LAHU MA TELEWTUHU ‘ALEJKUM WE LA ‘EDRAKUM BIHI FEKAD LEBITHTU FIKUM ‘UMURÆN MIN KABLIHI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  10,17,FEMEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EW KEDHDHEBE BI’AJATIHI ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHUL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,18,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JEDURRUHUM WE LA JENFA’UHUM WE JEKULUNE HA’UULA’ SHUFA’A’UUNA ‘INDEL-LAHI KUL ‘ETUNEBBI’UNEL-LAHE BIMA LA JA’LEMU FI ES-SEMAWATI WE LA FIL-’ERDI SUBHANEHU WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  10,19,WE MA KANE EN-NASU ‘ILLA ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN FAHTELEFU WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM FIMA FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  10,20,WE JEKULUNE LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI FEKUL ‘INNEMAL-GAJBU LILLAHI FANTEDHIRU ‘INNI ME’AKUM MINEL-MUNTEDHIRINE
  10,21,WE ‘IDHA ‘EDHEKNA EN-NASE REHMETEN MIN BA’DI DERRA’E MESSET/HUM ‘IDHA LEHUM MEKRUN FI ‘AJATINA KULI ELLAHU ‘ESRA’U MEKRÆN ‘INNE RUSULENA JEKTUBUNE MA TEMKURUN
  10,22,HUWEL-LEDHI JUSEJJIRUKUM FIL-BERRI WEL-BEHRI HETTA ‘IDHA KUNTUM FIL-FULKI WE XHEREJNE BIHIM BIRIHIN TEJJIBETIN WE FERIHU BIHA XHA’ET/HA RIHUN ‘ASIFUN WE XHA’EHUMUL-MEWXHU MIN KULLI MEKANIN WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHUM ‘UHITE BIHIM DE’AW ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DIN
  10,23,FELEMMA ‘ENXHAHUM ‘IDHA HUM JEBGUNE FIL-’ERDI BIGAJRIL-HEKKI JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNEMA BEGJUKUM ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIKUM META’AL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA THUMME ‘ILEJNA MERXHI’UKUM FENUNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  10,24,‘INNEMA METHELUL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA KEMA’IN ‘ENZELNAHU MINE ES-SEMA’I FAHTELETE BIHI NEBATUL-’ERDI MIMMA JE’KULU EN-NASU WEL-’EN’AM HETTA ‘IDHA ‘EHADHETIL-’ERDU ZUHRUFEHA WE EZZEJJENET WE DHENNE ‘EHLUHA ‘ENNEHUM KADIRUNE ‘ALEJHA ‘ETAHA ‘EMRUNA LEJLÆN ‘EW NEH
  10,25,WEL-LAHU JED’U ‘ILA DARI ES-SELAMI WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  10,26,LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENUL-HUSNA WE ZIJADETUN WE LA JERHEKU WUXHUHEHUM KATERUN WE LA DHILLETUN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  10,27,WEL-LEDHINE KESEBU ES-SEJJI’ATI XHEZA’U SEJJI’ETIN BIMITHLIHA WE TERHEKUHUM DHILLETUN MA LEHUM MINEL-LAHI MIN ‘ASIMIN KE’ENNEMA ‘UGSHIJET WUXHUHUHUM KITA’ÆN MINEL-LEJLI MUDHLIMÆN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  10,28,WE JEWME NEHSHURUHUM XHEMI’ÆN THUMME NEKULU LILLEDHINE ‘ESHREKU MEKANEKUM ‘ENTUM WE SHUREKA’UUKUM FEZEJJELNA BEJNEHUM WE KALE SHUREKA’UUHUM MA KUNTUM ‘IJANA TA’BUDUNE
  10,29,FEKEFA BILLAHI SHEHIDÆN BEJNENA WE BEJNEKUM ‘IN KUNNA ‘AN ‘IBADETIKUM LEGAFILINE
  10,30,HUNALIKE TEBLU KULLU NEFSIN MA ‘ESLEFET WE RUDDU ‘ILA ELLAHI MEWLAHUMUL-HEKKI WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  10,31,KUL MEN JERZUKUKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI ‘EMMEN JEMLIKU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WE MEN JUHRIXHUL-HEJJE MINEL-MEJJITI WE JUHRIXHUL-MEJJITE MINEL-HEJJI WE MEN JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE FESEJEKULUNEL-LAHU FEKUL ‘EFELA TETTEKUNE
  10,32,FEDHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUMUL-HEKKU FEMADHA BA’DEL-HEKKI ‘ILLA ED-DELALU FE’ENNA TUSREFUNE
  10,33,KEDHALIKE HEKKAT KELIMETU RABBIKE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE FESEKU ‘ENNEHUM LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,34,KUL HEL MIN SHUREKA’IKUM MEN JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU KULI ELLAHU JEBDE’UL-HALKA THUMME JU’IDUHU FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  10,35,KUL HEL MIN SHUREKA’IKUM MEN JEHDI ‘ILAL-HEKKI KULI ELLAHU JEHDI LILHEKKI ‘EFEMEN JEHDI ‘ILAL-HEKKI ‘EHEKKU ‘EN JUTTEBE’A ‘EMMEN LA JEHIDDI ‘ILLA ‘EN JUHDA FEMA LEKUM KEJFE TEHKUMUNE
  10,36,WE MA JETTEBI’U ‘EKTHERUHUM ‘ILLA DHENNÆN ‘INNE EDH-DHENNE LA JUGNI MINEL-HEKKI SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIMA JEF’ALUNE
  10,37,WE MA KANE HADHAL-KUR’ANU ‘EN JUFTERA MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE LEKIN TESDIKAL-LEDHI BEJNE JEDEJHI WE TEFSILEL-KITABI LA REJBE FIHI MIN RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  10,38,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL FE’TU BISURETIN MITHLIHI WE ED’U MENI ESTETA’TUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  10,39,BEL KEDHDHEBU BIMA LEM JUHITU BI’ILMIHI WE LEMMA JE’TIHIM TE’WILUHU KEDHALIKE KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETU EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,40,WE MINHUM MEN JU’UMINU BIHI WE MINHUM MEN LA JU’UMINU BIHI WE REBBUKE ‘A’LEMU BIL-MUFSIDINE
  10,41,WE ‘IN KEDHDHEBUKE FEKUL LI ‘AMELI WE LEKUM ‘AMELUKUM ‘ENTUM BERI’UNE MIMMA ‘A’MELU WE ‘ENA BERI’UN MIMMA TA’MELUNE
  10,42,WE MINHUM MEN JESTEMI’UNE ‘ILEJKE ‘EFE’ENTE TUSMI’U ES-SUMME WE LEW KANU LA JA’KILUNE
  10,43,WE MINHUM MEN JENDHURU ‘ILEJKE ‘EFE’ENTE TEHDIL-’UMJE WE LEW KANU LA JUBSIRUNE
  10,44,‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEDHLIMU EN-NASE SHEJ’ÆN WE LEKINNE EN-NASE ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  10,45,WE JEWME JEHSHURUHUM KE’EN LEM JELBETHU ‘ILLA SA’ATEN MINE EN-NEHARI JETA’AREFUNE BEJNEHUM KAD HASIREL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BILIKA’I ELLAHI WE MA KANU MUHTEDINE
  10,46,WE ‘IMMA NURIJENNEKE BA’DEL-LEDHI NA’IDUHUM ‘EW NETEWEFFEJENNEKE FE’ILEJNA MERXHI’UHUM THUMMEL-LAHU SHEHIDUN ‘ALA MA JEF’ALUNE
  10,47,WE LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN RESULUN FE’IDHA XHA’E RESULUHUM KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-KISTI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  10,48,WE JEKULUNE META HADHAL-WA’DU ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  10,49,KUL LA ‘EMLIKU LINEFSI DERRÆN WE LA NEF’ÆN ‘ILLA MA SHA’EL-LAHU LIKULLI ‘UMMETIN ‘EXHELUN ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHUM FELA JESTE’HIRUNE SA’ATEN WE LA JESTEKDIMUNE
  10,50,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN ‘ETAKUM ‘ADHABUHU BEJATÆN ‘EW NEHARÆN MADHA JESTA’XHILU MINHUL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,51,‘ETHUMME ‘IDHA MA WEKA’A ‘AMENTUM BIHI ‘AL’ANE WE KAD KUNTUM BIHI TESTA’XHILUNE
  10,52,THUMME KILE LILLEDHINE DHELEMU DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HULDI HEL TUXHZEWNE ‘ILLA BIMA KUNTUM TEKSIBUNE
  10,53,WE JESTENBI’UNEKE ‘EHEKKUN HUWE KUL ‘I WE RABBI ‘INNEHU LEHEKKUN WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  10,54,WE LEW ‘ENNE LIKULLI NEFSIN DHELEMET MA FIL-’ERDI LAFTEDET BIHI WE ‘ESERRU EN-NEDAMETE LEMMA RE’EWL-’ADHABE WE KUDIJE BEJNEHUM BIL-KISTI WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  10,55,‘ELA ‘INNE LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘ELA ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  10,56,HUWE JUHJI WE JUMITU WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  10,57,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU KAD XHA’ETKUM MEW’IDHETUN MIN RABBIKUM WE SHIFA’UN LIMA FI ES-SUDURI WE HUDEN WE REHMETUN LILMU’UMININE
  10,58,KUL BIFEDLI ELLAHI WE BIREHMETIHI FEBIDHALIKE FELJEFREHU HUWE HAJRUN MIMMA JEXHMA’UNE
  10,59,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU LEKUM MIN RIZKIN FEXHE’ALTUM MINHU HERAMÆN WE HELALÆN KUL ‘ALLLEHU ‘EDHINE LEKUM ‘EM ‘ALA ELLAHI TEFTERUNE
  10,60,WE MA DHENNUL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEDHU FEDLIN ‘ALA EN-NASI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHEREHUM LA JESHKURUNE
  10,61,WE MA TEKUNU FI SHE’NIN WE MA TETLU MINHU MIN KUR’ANIN WE LA TA’MELUNE MIN ‘AMELIN ‘ILLA KUNNA ‘ALEJKUM SHUHUDÆN ‘IDH TUFIDUNE FIHI WE MA JA’ZUBU ‘AN RABBIKE MIN MITHKALI DHERRETIN FIL-’ERDI WE LA FI ES-SEMA’I WE LA ‘ESGARE MIN DHALIKE WE LA ‘EKBERE ‘ILLA
  10,62,‘ELA ‘INNE ‘EWLIJA’EL-LAHI LA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  10,63,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE KANU JETTEKUNE
  10,64,LEHUMUL-BUSHRA FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE FIL-’AHIRETI LA TEBDILE LIKELIMATI ELLAHI DHALIKE HUWEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  10,65,WE LA JEHZUNKE KAWLUHUM ‘INNEL-’IZZETE LILLAHI XHEMI’ÆN HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  10,66,‘ELA ‘INNE LILLAHI MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MEN FIL-’ERDI WE MA JETTEBI’UL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI SHUREKA’E ‘IN JETTEBI’UNE ‘ILLA EDH-DHENNE WE ‘IN HUM ‘ILLA JEHRUSUNE
  10,67,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALE LEKUMUL-LEJLE LITESKUNU FIHI WE EN-NEHARE MUBSIRÆN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JESMA’UNE
  10,68,KALU ETTEHADHEL-LAHU WELEDÆN SUBHANEHU HUWEL-GANIJU LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI ‘IN ‘INDEKUM MIN SULTANIN BIHEDHA ‘ETEKULUNE ‘ALA ELLAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  10,69,KUL ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE LA JUFLIHUNE
  10,70,META’UN FI ED-DUNJA THUMME ‘ILEJNA MERXHI’UHUM THUMME NUDHIKUHUMUL-’ADHABE ESH-SHEDIDE BIMA KANU JEKFURUNE
  10,71,WE ETLU ‘ALEJHIM NEBE’E NUHIN ‘IDH KALE LIKAWMIHI JA KAWMI ‘IN KANE KEBURE ‘ALEJKUM MEKAMI WE TEDHKIRI BI’AJA TI ELLAHI FE’ALA ELLAHI TEWEKKELTU FE’EXHMI’U ‘EMREKUM WE SHUREKA’EKUM THUMME LA JEKUN ‘EMRUKUM ‘ALEJKUM GUMMETEN THUMME EKDU ‘ILEJJE WE LA TUNDH
  10,72,FE’IN TEWELLEJTUM FEMA SE’ELTUKUM MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN ‘EXHRI ‘ILLA ‘ALA ELLAHI WE ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘EKUNE MINEL-MUSLIMINE
  10,73,FEKEDHDHEBUHU FENEXHXHEJNAHU WE MEN ME’AHU FIL-FULKI WE XHE’ALNAHUM HALA’IFE WE ‘EGREKNAL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA FANDHUR KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUNDHERINE
  10,74,THUMME BE’ATHNA MIN BA’DIHI RUSULÆN ‘ILA KAWMIHIM FEXHA’UHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FEMA KANU LIJU’UMINU BIMA KEDHDHEBU BIHI MIN KABLU KEDHALIKE NETBA’U ‘ALA KULUBIL-MU’TEDINE
  10,75,THUMME BE’ATHNA MIN BA’DIHIM MUSA WE HARUNE ‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI BI’AJATINA FASTEKBERU WE KANU KAWMÆN MUXHRIMINE
  10,76,FELEMMA XHA’EHUMUL-HEKKU MIN ‘INDINA KALU ‘INNE HADHA LESIHRUN MUBINUN
  10,77,KALE MUSA ‘ETEKULUNE LILHEKKI LEMMA XHA’EKUM ‘ESIHRUN HADHA WE LA JUFLIHU ES-SAHIRUNE
  10,78,KALU ‘EXHI’TENA LITELFITENA ‘AMMA WEXHEDNA ‘ALEJHI ‘ABA’ENA WE TEKUNE LEKUMAL-KIBRIJA’U FIL-’ERDI WE MA NEHNU LEKUMA BIMU’UMININE
  10,79,WE KALE FIR’AWNU E’TUNI BIKULLI SAHIRIN ‘ALIMIN
  10,80,FELEMMA XHA’E ES-SEHERETU KALE LEHUM MUSA ‘ELKU MA ‘ENTUM MULKUNE
  10,81,FELEMMA ‘ELKAW KALE MUSA MA XHI’TUM BIHI ES-SIHRU ‘INNALL-LLAHE SEJUBTILUHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUSLIHU ‘AMELEL-MUFSIDINE
  10,82,WE JUHIKKU ELLAHUL-HEKKA BIKELIMATIHI WE LEW KERIHEL-MUXHRIMUNE
  10,83,FEMA ‘AMENE LIMUSA ‘ILLA DHURRIJETUN MIN KAWMIHI ‘ALA HAWFIN MIN FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHIM ‘EN JEFTINEHUM WE ‘INNE FIR’AWNE LA’ALIN FIL-’ERDI WE ‘INNEHU LEMINEL-MUSRIFINE
  10,84,WE KALE MUSA JA KAWMI ‘IN KUNTUM ‘AMENTUM BILLAHI FE’ALEJHI TEWEKKELU ‘IN KUNTUM MUSLIMINE
  10,85,FEKALU ‘ALA ELLAHI TEWEKKELNA REBBENA LA TEXH’ALNA FITNETEN LILKAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,86,WE NEXHXHINA BIREHMETIKE MINEL-KAWMIL-KAFIRINE
  10,87,WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILA MUSA WE ‘EHIHI ‘EN TEBEWWE’A LIKAWMIKUMA BIMISRE BUJUTÆN WE EXH’ALU BUJUTEKUM KIBLETEN WE ‘EKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE BESHSHIRIL-MU’UMININE
  10,88,WE KALE MUSA REBBENA ‘INNEKE ‘ATEJTE FIR’AWNE WE MELE’EHU ZINETEN WE ‘EMWALÆN FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA REBBENA LIJUDILLU ‘AN SEBILIKE REBBENA ETMIS ‘ALA ‘EMWALIHIM WE ESHDUD ‘ALA KULUBIHIM FELA JU’UMINU HETTA JEREWL-’ADHABEL-’ELIME
  10,89,KALE KAD ‘UXHIBET DA’WETUKUMA FASTEKIMA WE LA TETTEBI’ANI SEBILEL-LEDHINE LA JA’LEMUNE
  10,90,WE XHAWEZNA BIBENI ‘ISRA’ILEL-BEHRE FE’ETBE’AHUM FIR’AWNU WE XHUNUDUHU BEGJÆN WE’ADWEN HETTA ‘IDHA ‘EDREKEHUL-GAREKU KALE ‘AMENTU ‘ENNEHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLAL-LEDHI ‘AMENET BIHI BENU ‘ISRA’ILE WE ‘ENA MINEL-MUSLIMINE
  10,91,‘AL’ANE WE KAD ‘ASEJTE KABLU WE KUNTE MINEL-MUFSIDINE
  10,92,FALJEWME NUNEXHXHIKE BIBEDENIKE LITEKUNE LIMEN HALFEKE ‘AJETEN WE ‘INNE KETHIRÆN MINE EN-NASI ‘AN ‘AJATINA LEGAFILUNE
  10,93,WE LEKAD BEWWE’NA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE MUBEWWE’E SIDKIN WE REZEKNAHUM MINET-TEJJIBATI FEMA EHTELEFU HETTA XHA’EHUMUL-’ILMU ‘INNE REBBEKE JEKDI BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  10,94,FE’IN KUNTE FI SHEKKIN MIMMA ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKE FAS’ELIL-LEDHINE JEKRE’UNEL-KITABE MIN KABLIKE LEKAD XHA’EKEL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE FELA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUMTERINE
  10,95,WE LA TEKUNENNE MINEL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATI ELLAHI FETEKUNE MINEL-HASIRINE
  10,96,‘INNEL-LEDHINE HEKKAT ‘ALEJHIM KELIMETU RABBIKE LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,97,WE LEW XHA’ET/HUM KULLU ‘AJETIN HETTA JEREWL-’ADHABEL-’ELIME
  10,98,FELEWLA KANET KARJETUN ‘AMENET FENEFE’AHA ‘IMANUHA ‘ILLA KAWME JUNIS LEMMA ‘AMENU KESHEFNA ‘ANHUM ‘ADHABEL-HIZJI FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE METTA’NAHUM ‘ILA HININ
  10,99,WE LEW SHA’E REBBUKE LE’AMENE MEN FIL-’ERDI KULLUHUM XHEMI’ÆN ‘EFE’ENTE TUKRIHU EN-NASE HETTA JEKUNU MU’UMININE
  10,100,WE MA KANE LINEFSIN ‘EN TU’UMINE ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE JEXH’ALU ER-RIXHSE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE LA JA’KILUNE
  10,101,KUL ENDHURU MADHA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA TUGNIL-’AJATU WE EN-NUDHURU ‘AN KAWMIN LA JU’UMINUNE
  10,102,FEHEL JENTEDHIRUNE ‘ILLA MITHLE ‘EJJAMIL-LEDHINE HALEW MIN KABLIHIM KUL FANTEDHIRU ‘INNI ME’AKUM MINEL-MUNTEDHIRINE
  10,103,THUMME NUNEXHXHI RUSULENA WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU KEDHALIKE HEKKÆN ‘ALEJNA NUNXHIL-MU’UMININE
  10,104,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘IN KUNTUM FI SHEKKIN MIN DINI FELA ‘A’BUDUL-LEDHINE TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI WE LEKIN ‘A’BUDU ELLAHEL-LEDHI JETEWEFFAKUM WE ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘EKUNE MINEL-MU’UMININE
  10,105,WE ‘EN ‘EKIM WEXHHEKE LILDDINI HENIFÆN WE LA TEKUNENNE MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  10,106,WE LA TED’U MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JENFA’UKE WE LA JEDURRUKE FE’IN FE’ALTE FE’INNEKE ‘IDHÆN MINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  10,107,WE ‘IN JEMSESKEL-LAHU BIDURRIN FELA KASHIFE LEHU ‘ILLA HUWE WE ‘IN JURIDKE BIHAJRIN FELA RADDE LIFEDLIHI JUSIBU BIHI MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  10,108,KUL JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU KAD XHA’EKUMUL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKUM FEMENI EHTEDA FE’INNEMA JEHTEDI LINEFSIHI WE MEN DELLE FE’INNEMA JEDILLU ‘ALEJHA WE MA ‘ENA ‘ALEJKUM BIWEKILIN
  10,109,WE ETTEBI’ MA JUHA ‘ILEJKE WE ESBIR HETTA JEHKUMEL-LAHU WE HUWE HAJRUL-HAKIMINE
  11,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA KITABUN ‘UHKIMET ‘AJATUHU THUMME FUSSILET MIN LEDUN HEKIMIN HABIRIN
  11,2,‘ELLA TA’BUDU ‘ILLALLAHE ‘INNENI LEKUM MINHU NEDHIRUN WE BESHIRUN
  11,3,WE ‘ENI ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI JUMETTI’KUM META’ÆN HESENÆN ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN WE JU’UTI KULLE DHI FEDLIN FEDLEHU WE ‘IN TEWELLEW FE’INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN KEBIRIN
  11,4,‘ILA ELLAHI MERXHI’UKUM WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  11,5,‘ELA ‘INNEHUM JETHNUNE SUDUREHUM LIJESTEHFU MINHU ‘ELA HINE JESTEGSHUNE THIJABEHUM JA’LEMU MA JUSIRRUNE WE MA JU’LINUNE ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  11,6,WE MA MIN DABBETIN FIL-’ERDI ‘ILLA ‘ALA ELLAHI RIZKUHA WE JA’LEMU MUSTEKARREHA WE MUSTEWDE’AHA KULLUN FI KITABIN MUBININ
  11,7,WE HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE FI SITTETI ‘EJJAMIN WE KANE ‘ARSHUHU ‘ALEL-MA’I LIJEBLUWEKUM ‘EJJUKUM ‘EHSENU ‘AMELÆN WE LE’IN KULTE ‘INNEKUM MEB’UTHUNE MIN BA’DIL-MEWTI LEJEKULENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘IN HADHA ‘ILLA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  11,8,WE LE’IN ‘EHHARNA ‘ANHUMUL-’ADHABE ‘ILA ‘UMMETIN MA’DUDETIN LEJEKULUNNE MA JEHBISUHU ‘ELA JEWME JE’TIHIM LEJSE MESRUFÆN ‘ANHUM WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  11,9,WE LE’IN ‘EDHEKNAL-’INSANE MINNA REHMETEN THUMME NEZA’NAHA MINHU ‘INNEHU LEJE’USUN KEFURUN
  11,10,WE LE’IN ‘EDHEKNAHU NA’MA’E BA’DE DERRA’E MESSET/HU LEJEKULENNE DHEHEBE ES-SEJJI’ATU ‘ANNI ‘INNEHU LEFERIHUN FEHURUN
  11,11,‘ILLAL-LEDHINE SEBERU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE ‘EXHRUN KEBIRUN
  11,12,FELE’ALLEKE TARIKUN BA’DE MA JUHA ‘ILEJKE WE DA’IKUN BIHI SEDRUKE ‘EN JEKULU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI KENZUN ‘EW XHA’E ME’AHU MELEKUN ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE NEDHIRUN WEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN WE KILUN
  11,13,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL FE’TU BI’ASHRI SUWERIN MITHLIHI MUFTEREJATIN WE ED’U MENI ESTETA’TUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  11,14,FE’ILLEM JESTEXHIBU LEKUM FA’LEMU ‘ENNEMA ‘UNZILE BI’ILMI ELLAHI WE ‘EN LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE FEHEL ‘ENTUM MUSLIMUNE
  11,15,MEN KANE JURIDUL-HEJÆTE ED-DUNJA WE ZINETEHA NUWEFFI ‘ILEJHIM ‘A’MALEHUM FIHA WE HUM FIHA LA JUBHASUNE
  11,16,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE LEJSE LEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI ‘ILLA EN-NARU WE HEBITE MA SENA’U FIHA WE BATILUN MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  11,17,‘EFEMEN KANE ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBIHI WE JETLUHU SHAHIDUN MINHU WE MIN KABLIHI KITABU MUSA ‘IMAMÆN WE REHMETEN ‘ULA’IKE JU’UMINUNE BIHI WE MEN JEKFUR BIHI MINEL-’EHZABI FALNNARU MEW’IDUHU FELA TEKUN FI MIRJETIN MINHU ‘INNEHUL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE WE LEKIN
  11,18,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘ULA’IKE JU’REDUNE ‘ALA RABBIHIM WE JEKULUL-’ESH/HADU HA’UULA’L-LEDHINE KEDHEBU ‘ALA RABBIHIM ‘ELA LA’NETU ELLAHI ‘ALA EDH-DHALIMINE
  11,19,EL-LEDHINE JESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE JEBGUNEHA ‘IWEXHÆN WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI HUM KAFIRUNE
  11,20,‘ULA’IKE LEM JEKUNU MU’XHIZINE FIL-’ERDI WE MA KANE LEHUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN ‘EWLIJA’E JUDA’AFU LEHUMUL-’ADHABU MA KANU JESTETI’UNE ES-SEM’A WE MA KANU JUBSIRUNE
  11,21,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE HASIRU ‘ENFUSEHUM WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  11,22,LA XHEREME ‘ENNEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI HUMUL-’EHSERUNE
  11,23,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI WE ‘EHBETU ‘ILA RABBIHIM ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  11,24,METHELUL-FERIKAJNI KAL’A’MA WEL-’ESEMMI WEL-BESIRI WE ES-SEMI’I HEL JESTEWIJANI METHELÆN ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  11,25,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA NUHÆN ‘ILA KAWMIHI ‘INNI LEKUM NEDHIRUN MUBINUN
  11,26,‘EN LA TA’BUDU ‘ILLALLAHE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN ‘ELIMIN
  11,27,FEKALEL-MELE’UL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN KAWMIHI MA NERAKE ‘ILLA BESHERÆN MITHLENA WE MA NERAKE ETTEBE’AKE ‘ILLAL-LEDHINE HUM ‘ERADHILUNA BADIJE ER-RE’JI WE MA NERA LEKUM ‘ALEJNA MIN FEDLIN BEL NEDHUNNUKUM KADHIBINE
  11,28,KALE JA KAWMI ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KUNTU ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE ‘ATANI REHMETEN MIN ‘INDIHI FA’UMMIJET ‘ALEJKUM ‘ENULZIMUKUMUHA WE ‘ENTUM LEHA KARIHUNE
  11,29,WE JAKAWMI LA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI MALÆN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALA ELLAHI WE MA ‘ENA BITARIDIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘INNEHUM MULAKU RABBIHIM WE LEKINNI ‘ERAKUM KAWMÆN TEXHHELUNE
  11,30,WE JAKAWMI MEN JENSURUNI MINEL-LAHI ‘IN TEREDTUHUM ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  11,31,WE LA ‘EKULU LEKUM ‘INDI HAZA’INU ELLAHI WE LA ‘A’LEMUL-GAJBE WE LA ‘EKULU ‘INNI MELEKUN WE LA ‘EKULU LILLEDHINE TEZDERI ‘A’JUNUKUM LEN JU’UTIJEHUMU ELLAHU HAJRÆN ELLAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA FI ‘ENFUSIHIM ‘INNI ‘IDHÆN LEMINE EDH-DHALIMINE
  11,32,KALU JA NUHU KAD XHADELTENA FE’EKTHERTE XHIDALENA FE’TINA BIMA TA’IDUNA ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  11,33,KALE ‘INNEMA JE’TIKUM BIHI ELLAHU ‘IN SHA’E WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  11,34,WE LA JENFA’UKUM NUSHI ‘IN ‘EREDTU ‘EN ‘ENSEHE LEKUM ‘IN KANEL-LAHU JURIDU ‘EN JUGWIJEKUM HUWE REBBUKUM WE ‘ILEJHI TURXHA’UNE
  11,35,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU KUL ‘INI EFTEREJTUHU FE’ALEJJE ‘IXHRAMI WE ‘ENA BERI’UN MIMMA TUXHRIMUNE
  11,36,WE ‘UHIJE ‘ILA NUHIN ‘ENNEHU LEN JU’UMINE MIN KAWMIKE ‘ILLA MEN KAD ‘AMENE FELA TEBTE’IS BIMA KANU JEF’ALUNE
  11,37,WE ESNA’IL-FULKE BI’A’JUNINA WE WEHJINA WE LA TUHATIBNI FIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ‘INNEHUM MUGREKUNE
  11,38,WE JESNA’UL-FULKE WE KULLEMA MERRE ‘ALEJHI MELE’UN MIN KAWMIHI SEHIRU MINHU KALE ‘IN TESHARU MINNA FE’INNA NESHARU MINKUM KEMA TESHARUNE
  11,39,FESEWFE TA’LEMUNE MEN JE’TIHI ‘ADHABUN JUHZIHI WE JEHILLU ‘ALEJHI ‘ADHABUN MUKIMUN
  11,40,HETTA ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA WE FARET-TENNURU KULNA EHMIL FIHA MIN KULLIN ZEWXHEJNI ETHNEJNI WE ‘EHLEKE ‘ILLA MEN SEBEKA ‘ALEJHIL-KAWLU WE MEN ‘AMENE WE MA ‘AMENE ME’AHU ‘ILLA KALILUN
  11,41,WE KALE ERKEBU FIHA BISMI ELLAHI MEXHRAHA WE MURSAHA ‘INNE RABBI LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  11,42,WE HIJE TEXHRI BIHIM FI MEWXHIN KALXHIBALI WE NADA NUHUN EBNEHU WE KANE FI MA’ZILIN JA BUNEJJE ERKEB ME’ANA WE LA TEKUN ME’AL-KAFIRINE
  11,43,KALE SE’AWI ‘ILA XHEBELIN JA’SIMUNI MINEL-MA’I KALE LA ‘ASIMEL-JEWME MIN ‘EMRI ELLAHI ‘ILLA MEN REHIME WE HALE BEJNEHUMAL-MEWXHU FEKANE MINEL-MUGREKINE
  11,44,WE KILE JA ‘ERDU EBLA’I MA’EKI WE JA SEMA’U ‘EKLI’I WE GIDEL-MA’U WE KUDIJEL-’EMRU WE ESTEWET ‘ALEL-XHUDIJI WE KILE BU’DÆN LILKAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  11,45,WE NADA NUHUN REBBEHU FEKALE RABBI ‘INNE EBNI MIN ‘EHLI WE ‘INNE WA’DEKEL-HEKKU WE ‘ENTE ‘EHKEMUL-HAKIMINE
  11,46,KALE JA NUHU ‘INNEHU LEJSE MIN ‘EHLIKE ‘INNEHU ‘AMELUN GAJRU SALIHIN FELA TES’ELNI MA LEJSE LEKE BIHI ‘ILMUN ‘INNI ‘A’IDHUKE ‘EN TEKUNE MINEL-XHAHILINE
  11,47,KALE RABBI ‘INNI ‘A’UDHU BIKE ‘EN ‘ES’ELEKE MA LEJSE LI BIHI ‘ILMUN WE ‘ILLA TEGFIR LI WE TERHEMNI ‘EKUN MINEL-HASIRINE
  11,48,KILE JA NUHU EHBIT BISELAMIN MINNA WE BEREKATIN ‘ALEJKE WE ‘ALA ‘UMEMIN MIMMEN ME’AKE WE ‘UMEMUN SENUMETTI’UHUM THUMME JEMESSUHUM MINNA ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  11,49,TILKE MIN ‘ENBA’IL-GAJBI NUHIHA ‘ILEJKE MA KUNTE TA’LEMUHA ‘ENTE WE LA KAWMUKE MIN KABLI HADHA FASBIR ‘INNEL-’AKIBETE LILMUTTEKINE
  11,50,WE ‘ILA ‘ADIN ‘EHAHUM HUDÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA MUFTERUNE
  11,51,JA KAWMI LA ‘ES’ELUKUM ‘ALEJHI ‘EXHRÆN ‘IN ‘EXHRIJE ‘ILLA ‘ALEL-LEDHI FETERENI ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  11,52,WE JA KAWMI ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI JURSILI ES-SEMA’E ‘ALEJKUM MIDRARÆN WE JEZIDKUM KUWETEN ‘ILA KUWETIKUM WE LA TETEWELLEW MUXHRIMINE
  11,53,KALU JA HUDU MA XHI’TENA BIBEJJINETIN WE MA NEHNU BITARIKI ‘ALIHETINA ‘AN KAWLIKE WE MA NEHNU LEKE BIMU’UMININE
  11,54,‘IN NEKULU ‘ILLA A’TERAKE BA’DU ‘ALIHETINA BISU’IN KALE ‘INNI ‘USH/HIDU ELLAHE WE ESH/HEDU ‘ENNI BERI’UN MIMMA TUSHRIKUNE
  11,55,MIN DUNIHI FEKIDUNI XHEMI’ÆN THUMME LA TUNDHIRUNI
  11,56,‘INNI TEWEKKELTU ‘ALA ELLAHI RABBI WE RABBIKUM MA MIN DABBETIN ‘ILLA HUWE ‘AHIDHUN BINASIJETIHA ‘INNE RABBI ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  11,57,FE’IN TEWELLEW FEKAD ‘EBLEGTUKUM MA ‘URSILTU BIHI ‘ILEJKUM WE JESTEHLIFU RABBI KAWMÆN GAJREKUM WE LA TEDURRUNEHU SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNE RABBI ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN HEFIDHUN
  11,58,WE LEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA HUDÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE NEXHXHEJNAHUM MIN ‘ADHABIN GALIDHIN
  11,59,WE TILKE ‘ADUN XHEHEDU BI’AJATI RABBIHIM WE ‘ASEW RUSULEHU WE ETTEBA’U ‘EMRE KULLI XHEBBARIN ‘ANIDIN
  11,60,WE ‘UTBI’U FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA LA’NETEN WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘ELA ‘INNE ‘ADÆN KEFERU REBBEHUM ‘ELA BU’DÆN LI’ADIN KAWMI HUDIN
  11,61,WE ‘ILA THEMUDE ‘EHAHUM SALIHÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU HUWE ‘ENSHE’EKUM MINEL-’ERDI WE ESTA’MEREKUM FIHA FASTEGFIRUHU THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI ‘INNE RABBI KARIBUN MUXHIBUN
  11,62,KALU JA SALIHU KAD KUNTE FINA MERXHUWÆN KABLE HADHA ‘ETENHANA ‘EN NA’BUDE MA JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUNA WE ‘INNENA LEFI SHEKKIN MIMMA TED’UNA ‘ILEJHI MURIBIN
  11,63,KALE JA KAWMI ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KUNTU ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE ‘ATANI MINHU REHMETEN FEMEN JENSURUNI MINEL-LAHI ‘IN ‘ASEJTUHU FEMA TEZIDUNENI GAJRE TEHSIRIN
  11,64,WE JA KAWMI HEDHIHI NAKATU ELLAHI LEKUM ‘AJETEN FEDHERUHA TE’KUL FI ‘ERDI ELLAHI WE LA TEMESSUHA BISU’IN FEJE’HUDHEKUM ‘ADHABUN KARIBUN
  11,65,FE’AKARUHA FEKALE TEMETTA’U FI DARIKUM THELATHETE ‘EJJAMIN DHALIKE WA’DUN GAJRU MEKDHUBIN
  11,66,FELEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA SALIHÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE MIN HIZJI JEWMI’IDHIN ‘INNE REBBEKE HUWEL-KAWIJUL-’AZIZU
  11,67,WE ‘EHADHEL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ES-SEJHETU FE’ESBEHU FI DIJARIHIM XHATHIMINE
  11,68,KE’EN LEM JEGNEW FIHA ‘ELA ‘INNE THEMUDE KEFERU REBBEHUM ‘ELA BU’DÆN LITHEMUDE
  11,69,WE LEKAD XHA’ET RUSULUNA ‘IBRAHIME BIL-BUSHRA KALU SELAMÆN KALE SELAMUN FEMA LEBITHE ‘EN XHA’E BI’IXHLIN HENIDHIN
  11,70,FELEMMA RE’A ‘EJDIJEHUM LA TESILU ‘ILEJHI NEKIREHUM WE ‘EWXHESE MINHUM HIFETEN KALU LA TEHAF ‘INNA ‘URSILNA ‘ILA KAWMI LUTIN
  11,71,WE EMRE’ETUHU KA’IMETUN FEDEHIKET FEBESHSHERNAHA BI’ISHAKA WE MIN WERA’I ‘ISHAKA JA’KUBE
  11,72,KALET JA WEJLETA ‘E’ELIDU WE ‘ENA ‘AXHUZUN WE HEDHA BA’LI SHEJHÆN ‘INNE HADHA LESHEJ’UN ‘AXHIBUN
  11,73,KALU ‘ETA’XHEBINE MIN ‘EMRI ELLAHI REHMETU ELLAHI WE BEREKATUHU ‘ALEJKUM ‘EHLEL-BEJTI ‘INNEHU HEMIDUN MEXHIDUN
  11,74,FELEMMA DHEHEBE ‘AN ‘IBRAHIME ER-REW’U WE XHA’ET/HUL-BUSHRA JUXHADILUNA FI KAWMI LUTIN
  11,75,‘INNE ‘IBRAHIME LEHELIMUN ‘EWWAHUN MUNIBUN
  11,76,JA ‘IBRAHIMU ‘A’RID ‘AN HADHA ‘INNEHU KAD XHA’E ‘EMRU RABBIKE WE ‘INNEHUM ‘ATIHIM ‘ADHABUN GAJRU MERDUDIN
  11,77,WE LEMMA XHA’ET RUSULUNA LUTÆN SI’E BIHIM WE DAKA BIHIM DHER’ÆN WE KALE HADHA JEWMUN ‘ASIBUN
  11,78,WE XHA’EHU KAWMUHU JUHRA’UNE ‘ILEJHI WE MIN KABLU KANU JA’MELUNE ES-SEJJI’ATI KALE JA KAWMI HA’UULA’ BENATI HUNNE ‘ETHERU LEKUM FE ETTEKU ELLAHE WE LA TUHZUNI FI DEJFI ‘ELEJSE MINKUM REXHULUN RESHIDUN
  11,79,KALU LEKAD ‘ALIMTE MA LENA FI BENATIKE MIN HEKKIN WE ‘INNEKE LETA’LEMU MA NURIDU
  11,80,KALE LEW ‘ENNE LI BIKUM KUWETEN ‘EW ‘AWI ‘ILA RUKNIN SHEDIDIN
  11,81,KALU JA LUTU ‘INNA RUSULU RABBIKE LEN JESILU ‘ILEJKE FE’ESRI BI’EHLIKE BIKIT’IN MINEL-LEJLI WE LA JELTEFIT MINKUM ‘EHEDUN ‘ILLA EMRE’ETEKE ‘INNEHU MUSIBUHA MA ‘ESABEHUM ‘INNE MEW’IDEHUMU ES-SUBHU ‘ELEJSE ES-SUBHU BIKARIBIN
  11,82,FELEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA XHE’ALNA ‘ALIJEHA SAFILEHA WE ‘EMTERNA ‘ALEJHA HIXHARETEN MIN SIXHXHILIN MENDUDIN
  11,83,MUSEWWEMETEN ‘INDE RABBIKE WE MA HIJE MINE EDH-DHALIMINE BIBA’IDIN
  11,84,WE ‘ILA MEDJENE ‘EHAHUM SHU’AJBÆN KALE JA KAWMI A’BUDU ELLAHE MA LEKUM MIN ‘ILEHIN GAJRUHU WE LA TENKUSUL-MIKJA LE WEL-MIZANE ‘INNI ‘ERAKUM BIHAJRIN WE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ‘ALEJKUM ‘ADHABE JEWMIN MUHITIN
  11,85,WE JA KAWMI ‘EWFUL-MIKJALE WEL-MIZANE BIL-KISTI WE LA TEBHASU EN-NASE ‘ESHJA’EHUM WE LA TA’THEW FIL-’ERDI MUFSIDINE
  11,86,BEKIJETU ELLAHI HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE WE MA ‘ENA ‘ALEJKUM BIHEFIDHIN
  11,87,KALU JA SHU’AJBU ‘ESELATUKE TE’MURUKE ‘EN NETRUKE MA JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUNA ‘EW ‘EN NEF’ALE FI ‘EMWALINA MA NESHA’U ‘INNEKE LE’ENTEL-HELIMU ER-RESHIDU
  11,88,KALE JA KAWMI ‘ERE’EJTUM ‘IN KUNTU ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MIN RABBI WE REZEKANI MINHU RIZKÆN HESENÆN WE MA ‘URIDU ‘EN ‘UHALIFEKUM ‘ILA MA ‘ENHAKUM ‘ANHU ‘IN ‘URIDU ‘ILLAL-’ISLAHE MA ESTETA’TU WE MA TEWFIKI ‘ILLA BILLAHI ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELTU WE ‘ILEJHI ‘UNIBU
  11,89,WE JA KAWMI LA JEXHRIMENNEKUM SHIKAKI ‘EN JUSIBEKUM MITHLU MA ‘ESABE KAWME NUHIN ‘EW KAWME HUDIN ‘EW KAWME SALIHIN WE MA KAWMU LUTIN MINKUM BIBA’IDIN
  11,90,WE ESTEGFIRU REBBEKUM THUMME TUBU ‘ILEJHI ‘INNE RABBI REHIMUN WEDUDUN
  11,91,KALU JA SHU’AJBU MA NEFKAHU KETHIRÆN MIMMA TEKULU WE ‘INNA LENERAKE FINA DA’IFÆN WE LEWLA REHTUKE LEREXHEMNAKE WE MA ‘ENTE ‘ALEJNA BI’AZIZIN
  11,92,KALE JA KAWMI ‘EREHTI ‘E’AZZU ‘ALEJKUM MINEL-LAHI WE ETTEHADHTUMUHU WERA’EKUM DHIHRIJÆN ‘INNE RABBI BIMA TA’MELUNE MUHITUN
  11,93,WE JA KAWMI A’MELU ‘ALA MEKANETIKUM ‘INNI ‘AMILUN SEWFE TA’LEMUNE MEN JE’TIHI ‘ADHABUN JUHZIHI WE MEN HUWE KADHIBUN WE ERTEKIBU ‘INNI ME’AKUM REKIBUN
  11,94,WE LEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRUNA NEXHXHEJNA SHU’AJBÆN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU BIREHMETIN MINNA WE ‘EHADHETIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ES-SEJHETU FE’ESBEHU FI DIJARIHIM XHATHIMINE
  11,95,KE’EN LEM JEGNEW FIHA ‘ELA BU’DÆN LIMEDJENE KEMA BA’IDET THEMUDU
  11,96,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA MUSA BI’AJATINA WE SULTANIN MUBININ
  11,97,‘ILA FIR’AWNE WE MELE’IHI FE ETTEBA’U ‘EMRE FIR’AWNE WE MA ‘EMRU FIR’AWNE BIRESHIDIN
  11,98,JEKDUMU KAWMEHU JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FE’EWREDEHUMU EN-NARE WE BI’SEL-WIRDUL-MEWRUDU
  11,99,WE ‘UTBI’U FI HEDHIHI LA’NETEN WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI BI’SE ER-RIFDUL-MERFUDU
  11,100,DHALIKE MIN ‘ENBA’IL-KURA NEKUSSUHU ‘ALEJKE MINHA KA’IMUN WE HESIDUN
  11,101,WE MA DHELEMNAHUM WE LEKIN DHELEMU ‘ENFUSEHUM FEMA ‘EGNET ‘ANHUM ‘ALIHETUHUMU ELLETI JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN LEMMA XHA’E ‘EMRU RABBIKE WE MA ZADUHUM GAJRE TETBIBIN
  11,102,WE KEDHELIKE ‘EHDHU RABBIKE ‘IDHA ‘EHADHEL-KURA WE HIJE DHALIMETUN ‘INNE ‘EHDHEHU ‘ELIMUN SHEDIDUN
  11,103,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIMEN HAFE ‘ADHABEL-’AHIRETI DHALIKE JEWMUN MEXHMU’UN LEHU EN-NASU WE DHELIKE JEWMUN MESH/HUDUN
  11,104,WE MA NU’UEHHIRUHU ‘ILLA LI’XHELIN MA’DUDIN
  11,105,JEWME JE’TI LA TEKELLEMU NEFSUN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNIHI FEMINHUM SHEKIJUN WE SA’IDUN
  11,106,FE’EMMAL-LEDHINE SHEKU FEFI EN-NARI LEHUM FIHA ZEFIRUN WE SHEHIKUN
  11,107,HALIDINE FIHA MA DAMETI ES-SEMAWATU WEL-’ERDU ‘ILLA MA SHA’E REBBUKE ‘INNE REBBEKE FA’’ALUN LIMA JURIDU
  11,108,WE ‘EMMAL-LEDHINE SU’IDU FEFIL-XHENNETI HALIDINE FIHA MA DAMETI ES-SEMAWATU WEL-’ERDU ‘ILLA MA SHA’E REBBUKE ‘ATA’EN GAJRE MEXHDHUDHIN
  11,109,FELA TEKU FI MIRJETIN MIMMA JA’BUDU HA’UULA’ MA JA’BUDUNE ‘ILLA KEMA JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUHUM MIN KABLU WE ‘INNA LEMUWEFFUHUM NESIBEHUM GAJRE MENKUSIN
  11,110,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNA MUSAL-KITABE FAHTULIFE FIHI WE LEWLA KELIMETUN SEBEKAT MIN RABBIKE LEKUDIJE BEJNEHUM WE ‘INNEHUM LEFI SHEKKIN MINHU MURIBIN
  11,111,WE ‘INNE KULLA LEMMA LEJUWEFFIJENNEHUM REBBUKE ‘A’MALEHUM ‘INNEHU BIMA JA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  11,112,FASTEKIM KEMA ‘UMIRTE WE MEN TABE ME’AKE WE LA TETGAW ‘INNEHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  11,113,WE LA TERKENU ‘ILAL-LEDHINE DHELEMU FETEMESSEKUMU EN-NARU WE MA LEKUM MIN DUNI ELLAHI MIN ‘EWLIJA’E THUMME LA TUNSERUNE
  11,114,WE ‘EKIMI ES-SELÆTE TEREFEJI EN-NEHARI WE ZULEFÆN MINEL-LEJLI ‘INNEL-HESENATI JUDH/HIBNE ES-SEJJI’ATI DHALIKE DHIKRA LILDHDHAKIRINE
  11,115,WE ESBIR FE’INNALL-LLAHE LA JUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MUHSININE
  11,116,FELEWLA KANE MINEL-KURUNI MIN KABLIKUM ‘ULU BEKIJETIN JENHEWNE ‘ANIL-FESADI FIL-’ERDI ‘ILLA KALILÆN MIMMEN ‘ENXHEJNA MINHUM WE ETTEBE’AL-LEDHINE DHELEMU MA ‘UTRIFU FIHI WE KANU MUXHRIMINE
  11,117,WE MA KANE REBBUKE LIJUHLIKEL-KURA BIDHULMIN WE ‘EHLUHA MUSLIHUNE
  11,118,WE LEW SHA’E REBBUKE LEXHE’ALE EN-NASE ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN WE LA JEZALUNE MUHTELIFINE
  11,119,‘ILLA MEN REHIME REBBUKE WE LIDHELIKE HALEKAHUM WE TEMMET KELIMETU RABBIKE LE’EMLE’ENNE XHEHENNEME MINEL-XHINNETI WE EN-NASI ‘EXHMA’INE
  11,120,WE KULLÆN NEKUSSU ‘ALEJKE MIN ‘ENBA’I ER-RUSULI MA NUTHEBBITU BIHI FU’UADEKE WE XHA’EKE FI HEDHIHIL-HEKKU WE MEW’IDHETUN WE DHIKRA LILMU’UMININE
  11,121,WE KUL LILLEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE A’MELU ‘ALA MEKANETIKUM ‘INNA ‘AMILUNE
  11,122,WE ENTEDHIRU ‘INNA MUNTEDHIRUNE
  11,123,WE LILLEHI GAJBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE ‘ILEJHI JURXHA’UL-’EMRU KULLUHU FA’BUD/HU WE TEWEKKEL ‘ALEJHI WE MA REBBUKE BIGAFILIN ‘AMMA TA’MELUNE
  12,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABIL-MUBINI
  12,2,‘INNA ‘ENZELNAHU KUR’ANÆN ‘AREBIJÆN LE’ALLEKUM TA’KILUNE
  12,3,NEHNU NEKUSSU ‘ALEJKE ‘EHSENEL-KASESI BIMA ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE HADHAL-KUR’ANE WE ‘IN KUNTE MIN KABLIHI LEMINEL-GAFILINE
  12,4,‘IDH KALE JUSUFU LI’EBIHI JA ‘EBETI ‘INNI RE’EJTU ‘EHEDE ‘ASHERE KEWKEBÆN WE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE RE’EJTUHUM LI SAXHIDINE
  12,5,KALE JA BUNEJJE LA TEKSUS RU’UJA KE ‘ALA ‘IHWETIKE FEJEKIDU LEKE KEJDÆN ‘INNE ESH-SHEJTANE LIL’INSANI ‘ADUWUN MUBINUN
  12,6,WE KEDHELIKE JEXHTEBIKE REBBUKE WE JU’ALLIMUKE MIN TE’WILIL-’EHADITHI WE JUTIMMU NI’METEHU ‘ALEJKE WE ‘ALA ‘ALI JA’KUBE KEMA ‘ETEMMEHA ‘ALA ‘EBEWEJKE MIN KABLU ‘IBRAHIME WE ‘ISHAKA ‘INNE REBBEKE ‘ALIMUN HEKIMUN
  12,7,LEKAD KANE FI JUSUFE WE ‘IHWETIHI ‘AJATUN LILSSA’ILINE
  12,8,‘IDH KALU LEJUSUFU WE ‘EHUHU ‘EHEBBU ‘ILA ‘EBINA MINNA WE NEHNU ‘USBETUN ‘INNE ‘EBANA LEFI DELALIN MUBININ
  12,9,EKTULU JUSUFE ‘EWI ETREHUHU ‘ERDÆN JEHLU LEKUM WEXHHU ‘EBIKUM WE TEKUNU MIN BA’DIHI KAWMÆN SALIHINE
  12,10,KALE KA’ILUN MINHUM LA TEKTULU JUSUFE WE ‘ELKUHU FI GAJABETIL-XHUBBI JELTEKITHU BA’DU ES-SEJJARETI ‘IN KUNTUM FA’ILINE
  12,11,KALU JA ‘EBANA MA LEKE LA TE’MENNA ‘ALA JUSUFE WE ‘INNA LEHU LENASIHUNE
  12,12,‘ERSILHU ME’ANA GADÆN JERTA’ WE JEL’AB WE ‘INNA LEHU LEHAFIDHUNE
  12,13,KALE ‘INNI LEJEHZUNUNI ‘EN TEDH/HEBU BIHI WE ‘EHAFU ‘EN JE’KULEHU EDH-DHI’BU WE ‘ENTUM ‘ANHU GAFILUNE
  12,14,KALU LE’IN ‘EKELEHU EDH-DHI’BU WE NEHNU ‘USBETUN ‘INNA ‘IDHÆN LEHASIRUNE
  12,15,FELEMMA DHEHEBU BIHI WE ‘EXHMA’U ‘EN JEXH’ALUHU FI GAJABETIL-XHUBBI WE ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJHI LETUNEBBI’ENNEHUM BI’EMRIHIM HADHA WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  12,16,WE XHA’U ‘EBAHUM ‘ISHA’EN JEBKUNE
  12,17,KALU JA ‘EBANA ‘INNA DHEHEBNA NESTEBIKU WE TEREKNA JUSUFE ‘INDE META’INA FE’EKELEHU EDH-DHI’BU WE MA ‘ENTE BIMU’UMININ LENA WE LEW KUNNA SADIKINE
  12,18,WE XHA’U ‘ALA KAMISIHI BIDEMIN KEDHIBIN KALE BEL SEWWELET LEKUM ‘ENFUSUKUM ‘EMRÆN FESEBRUN XHEMILUN WEL-LAHUL-MUSTA’ANU ‘ALA MA TESIFUNE
  12,19,WE XHA’ET SEJJARETUN FE’ERSELU WE ERIDEHUM FE’EDLA DELWEHU KALE JA BUSHRA HADHA GULAMUN WE ‘ESERRUHU BIDA’ATEN WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN BIMA JA’MELUNE
  12,20,WE SHEREWHU BITHEMENIN BEHSIN DERAHIME MA’DUDETIN WE KANU FIHI MINE EZ-ZAHIDINE
  12,21,WE KALEL-LEDHI ESHTERAHU MIN MISRE LI’IMRE’ETIHI ‘EKRIMI METHWAHU ‘ASA ‘EN JENFE’ANA ‘EW NETTEHIDHEHU WELEDÆN WE KEDHELIKE MEKKENNA LIJUSUFE FIL-’ERDI WE LINU’ALLIMEHU MIN TE’WILIL-’EHADITHI WEL-LAHU GALIBUN ‘ALA ‘EMRIHI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’
  12,22,WE LEMMA BELEGA ‘ESHUDDEHU ‘ATEJNAHU HUKMÆN WE ‘ILMÆN WE KEDHELIKE NEXHZIL-MUHSININE
  12,23,WE RAWEDET/HU ELLETI HUWE FI BEJTIHA ‘AN NEFSIHI WE GALLEKATIL-’EBWABE WE KALET HEJTE LEKE KALE MA’ADHEL-LAHI ‘INNEHU RABBI ‘EHSENE METHWAJE ‘INNEHU LA JUFLIHU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  12,24,WE LEKAD HEMMET BIHI WE HEMME BIHA LEWLA ‘EN RE’A BURHANE RABBIHI KEDHALIKE LINESRIFE ‘ANHU ES-SU’E WEL-FEHSHA’E ‘INNEHU MIN ‘IBADINAL-MUHLESINE
  12,25,WE ESTEBEKAL-BABE WE KADDET KAMISEHU MIN DUBURIN WE ‘ELFEJA SEJJIDEHA LEDAL-BABI KALET MA XHEZA’U MEN ‘ERADE BI’EHLIKE SU’ÆN ‘ILLA ‘EN JUSXHENE ‘EW ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  12,26,KALE HIJE RAWEDETNI ‘AN NEFSI WE SHEHIDE SHAHIDUN MIN ‘EHLIHA ‘IN KANE KAMISUHU KUDDE MIN KUBULIN FESEDEKAT WE HUWE MINEL-KADHIBINE
  12,27,WE ‘IN KANE KAMISUHU KUDDE MIN DUBURIN FEKEDHEBET WE HUWE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  12,28,FELEMMA RE’A KAMISEHU KUDDE MIN DUBURIN KALE ‘INNEHU MIN KEJDIKUNNE ‘INNE KEJDEKUNNE ‘ADHIMUN
  12,29,JUSUFU ‘A’RID ‘AN HADHA WE ESTEGFIRI LIDHENBIKI ‘INNEKI KUNTI MINEL-HATI’INE
  12,30,WE KALE NISWETUN FIL-MEDINETI EMRE’ETUL-’AZIZI TURAWIDU FETAHA ‘AN NEFSIHI KAD SHEGAFEHA HUBBÆN ‘INNA LENERAHA FI DELALIN MUBININ
  12,31,FELEMMA SEMI’AT BIMEKRIHINNE ‘ERSELET ‘ILEJHINNE WE ‘A’TEDET LEHUNNE MUTTEKE’EN WE ‘ATET KULLE WAHIDETIN MINHUNNE SIKKINÆN WE KALETI EHRUXH ‘ALEJHINNE FELEMMA RE’EJNEHU ‘EKBERNEHU WE KATTA’NE ‘EJDIJEHUNNE WE KULNE HASHE LILLAHI MA HADHA BESHERÆN ‘IN HADHA
  12,32,KALET FEDHALIKUNNEL-LEDHI LUMTUNNENI FIHI WE LEKAD RAWEDTTUHU ‘AN NEFSIHI FASTA’SEME WE LE’IN LEM JEF’AL MA ‘AMURUHU LEJUSXHENENNE WE LEJEKUNÆN MINE ES-SAGIRINE
  12,33,KALE RABBI ES-SIXHNU ‘EHEBBU ‘ILEJJE MIMMA JED’UNENI ‘ILEJHI WE ‘ILLA TESRIF ‘ANNI KEJDEHUNNE ‘ESBU ‘ILEJHINNE WE ‘EKUN MINEL-XHAHILINE
  12,34,FASTEXHABE LEHU REBBUHU FESEREFE ‘ANHU KEJDEHUNNE ‘INNEHU HUWE ES-SEMI’UL-’ALIMU
  12,35,THUMME BEDA LEHUM MIN BA’DI MA RE’EWL-’AJATI LEJESXHUNUNNEHU HETTA HININ
  12,36,WE DEHALE ME’AHU ES-SIXHNE FETEJANI KALE ‘EHEDUHUMA ‘INNI ‘ERANI ‘A’SIRU HAMRÆN WE KALEL-’AHARU ‘INNI ‘ERANI ‘EHMILU FEWKA RE’SI HUBZÆN TE’KULUT-TEJRU MINHU NEBBI’NA BITE’WILIHI ‘INNA NERAKE MINEL-MUHSININE
  12,37,KALE LA JE’TIKUMA TA’AMUN TURZEKANIHI ‘ILLA NEBBE’TUKUMA BITE’WILIHI KABLE ‘EN JE’TIJEKUMA DHALIKUMA MIMMA ‘ALLEMENI RABBI ‘INNI TEREKTU MILLETE KAWMIN LA JU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WE HUM BIL-’AHIRETI HUM KAFIRUNE
  12,38,WE ETTEBA’TU MILLETE ‘ABA’I ‘IBRAHIME WE ‘ISHAKA WE JA’KUBE MA KANE LENA ‘EN NUSHRIKE BILLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN DHALIKE MIN FEDLI ELLAHI ‘ALEJNA WE ‘ALA EN-NASI WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JESHKURUNE
  12,39,JA SAHIBEJI ES-SIXHNI ‘E’ERBABUN MUTEFERRIKUNE HAJRUN ‘EMI ELLAHUL-WAHIDUL-KAHHARU
  12,40,MA TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNIHI ‘ILLA ‘ESMA’EN SEMMEJTUMUHA ‘ENTUM WE ‘ABA’UUKUM MA ‘ENZELEL-LAHU BIHA MIN SULTANIN ‘INIL-HUKMU ‘ILLA LILLAHI ‘EMERE ‘ELLA TA’BUDU ‘ILLA ‘IJAHU DHALIKE ED-DINUL-KAJJIMU WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  12,41,JA SAHIBEJI ES-SIXHNI ‘EMMA ‘EHEDUKUMA FEJESKI REBBEHU HAMRÆN WE ‘EMMAL-’AHARU FEJUSLEBU FETE’KULUT-TEJRU MIN RE’SIHI KUDIJEL-’EMRUL-LEDHI FIHI TESTEFTIJANI
  12,42,WE KALE LILLEDHI DHENNE ‘ENNEHU NAXHIN MINHUMA EDHKURNI ‘INDE RABBIKE FE’ENSAHU ESH-SHEJTANU DHIKRE RABBIHI FELEBITHE FI ES-SIXHNI BID’A SININE
  12,43,WE KALEL-MELIKU ‘INNI ‘ERA SEB’A BEKARATIN SIMANIN JE’KULUHUNNE SEB’UN ‘IXHAFUN WE SEB’A SUNBULATIN HUDRIN WE ‘UHARE JA BISATIN JA ‘EJJUHAL-MELE’U ‘EFTUNI FI RU’UJA JE ‘IN KUNTUM LILRRU’UJA TA’BURUNE
  12,44,KALU ‘EDGATHU ‘EHLAMIN WE MA NEHNU BITE’WILIL-’EHLAMI BI’ALIMINE
  12,45,WE KALEL-LEDHI NEXHA MINHUMA WE EIDDEKERE BA’DE ‘UMMETIN ‘ENA ‘UNEBBI’UKUM BITE’WILIHI FE’ERSILUNI
  12,46,JUSUFU ‘EJJUHA ES-SIDDIKU ‘EFTINA FI SEB’I BEKARATIN SIMANIN JE’KULUHUNNE SEB’UN ‘IXHAFUN WE SEB’I SUNBULATIN HUDRIN WE ‘UHARE JA BISATIN LE’ALLI ‘ERXHI’U ‘ILA EN-NASI LE’ALLEHUM JA’LEMUNE
  12,47,KALE TEZRA’UNE SEB’A SININE DE’EBÆN FEMA HESEDTUM FEDHERUHU FI SUNBULIHI ‘ILLA KALILÆN MIMMA TE’KULUNE
  12,48,THUMME JE’TI MIN BA’DI DHALIKE SEB’UN SHIDADUN JE’KULNE MA KADDEMTUM LEHUNNE ‘ILLA KALILÆN MIMMA TUHSINUNE
  12,49,THUMME JE’TI MIN BA’DI DHALIKE ‘AMUN FIHI JUGATHU EN-NASU WE FIHI JA’SIRUNE
  12,50,WE KALEL-MELIKU E’TUNI BIHI FELEMMA XHA’EHU ER-RESULU KALE ERXHI’ ‘ILA RABBIKE FAS’ELHU MA BALU EN-NISWETIL-LATI KATTA’NE ‘EJDIJEHUNNE ‘INNE RABBI BIKEJDIHINNE ‘ALIMUN
  12,51,KALE MA HATBUKUNNE ‘IDH RAWEDTTUNNE JUSUFE ‘AN NEFSIHI KULNE HASHE LILLAHI MA ‘ALIMNA ‘ALEJHI MIN SU’IN KALETI EMRE’ETUL-’AZIZIL-’ANE HESHESEL-HEKKU ‘ENA RAWEDTTUHU ‘AN NEFSIHI WE ‘INNEHU LEMINE ES-SADIKINE
  12,52,DHALIKE LIJA’LEME ‘ENNI LEM ‘EHUNHU BIL-GAJBI WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LA JEHDI KEJDEL-HA’ININE
  12,53,WE MA ‘UBERRI’U NEFSI ‘INNE EN-NEFSE LE’EMMARETUN BIS-SU’I ‘ILLA MA REHIME RABBI ‘INNE RABBI GAFURUN REHIMUN
  12,54,WE KALEL-MELIKU E’TUNI BIHI ‘ESTEHLISHU LINEFSI FELEMMA KELLEMEHU KALE ‘INNEKEL-JEWME LEDEJNA MEKINUN ‘EMINUN
  12,55,KALE EXH’ALNI ‘ALA HAZA’INIL-’ERDI ‘INNI HEFIDHUN ‘ALIMUN
  12,56,WE KEDHELIKE MEKKENNA LIJUSUFE FIL-’ERDI JETEBEWWE’U MINHA HEJTHU JESHA’U NUSIBU BIREHMETINA MEN NESHA’U WE LA NUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MUHSININE
  12,57,WE LE’EXHRUL-’AHIRETI HAJRUN LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU WE KANU JETTEKUNE
  12,58,WE XHA’E ‘IHWETU JUSUFE FEDEHALU ‘ALEJHI FE’AREFEHUM WE HUM LEHU MUNKIRUNE
  12,59,WE LEMMA XHEHHEZEHUM BIXHEHAZIHIM KALE E’TUNI BI’EHIN LEKUM MIN ‘EBIKUM ‘ELA TEREWNE ‘ENNI ‘UFIL-KEJLE WE ‘ENA HAJRUL-MUNZILINE
  12,60,FE’IN LEM TE’TUNI BIHI FELA KEJLE LEKUM ‘INDI WE LA TEKREBUNI
  12,61,KALU SENURAWIDU ‘ANHU ‘EBAHU WE ‘INNA LEFA’ILUNE
  12,62,WE KALE LIFITJANIHI EXH’ALU BIDA’ATEHUM FI RIHALIHIM LE’ALLEHUM JA’RIFUNEHA ‘IDHA ENKALEBU ‘ILA ‘EHLIHIM LE’ALLEHUM JERXHI’UNE
  12,63,FELEMMA REXHA’U ‘ILA ‘EBIHIM KALU JA ‘EBANA MUNI’A MINNAL-KEJLU FE’ERSIL ME’ANA ‘EHANA NEKTEL WE ‘INNA LEHU LEHAFIDHUNE
  12,64,KALE HEL ‘AMENUKUM ‘ALEJHI ‘ILLA KEMA ‘EMINTUKUM ‘ALA ‘EHIHI MIN KABLU FE-ELLAHU HAJRUN HAFIDHÆN WE HUWE ‘ERHEMU ER-RAHIMINE
  12,65,WE LEMMA FETEHU META’AHUM WE XHEDU BIDA’ATEHUM RUDDET ‘ILEJHIM KALU JA ‘EBANA MA NEBGI HEDHIHI BIDA’ATUNA RUDDET ‘ILEJNA WE NEMIRU ‘EHLENA WE NEHFEDHU ‘EHANA WE NEZDADU KEJLE BA’IRIN DHALIKE KEJLUN JESIRUN
  12,66,KALE LEN ‘URSILEHU ME’AKUM HETTA TU’UTUNI MEWTHIKÆN MINEL-LAHI LETE’TUNENI BIHI ‘ILLA ‘EN JUHATE BIKUM FELEMMA ‘ATEWHU MEWTHIKAHUM KALEL-LAHU ‘ALA MA NEKULU WE KILUN
  12,67,WE KALE JA BENIJE LA TEDHULU MIN BABIN WAHIDIN WE EDHULU MIN ‘EBWABIN MUTEFERRIKATIN WE MA ‘UGNI ‘ANKUM MINEL-LAHI MIN SHEJ’IN ‘INIL-HUKMU ‘ILLA LILLAHI ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELTU WE ‘ALEJHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MUTEWEKKILUNE
  12,68,WE LEMMA DEHALU MIN HEJTHU ‘EMEREHUM ‘EBUHUM MMA KANE JUGNI ‘ANHUM MMINEL-LAHI MIN SHEJ’IN ‘ILLA HAXHETEN FI NEFSI JA’KUBE KADAHA WE ‘INNEHU LEDHU ‘ILMIN LIMA ‘ALLEMNAHU WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  12,69,WE LEMMA DEHALU ‘ALA JUSUFE ‘AWA ‘ILEJHI ‘EHAHU KALE ‘INNI ‘ENA ‘EHUKE FELA TEBTE’IS BIMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  12,70,FELEMMA XHEHHEZEHUM BIXHEHAZIHIM XHE’ALE ES-SIKAJETE FI REHLI ‘EHIHI THUMME ‘EDHDHENE MU’UEDHDHINUN ‘EJJETUHAL-’IRU ‘INNEKUM LESARIKUNE
  12,71,KALU WE ‘EKBELU ‘ALEJHIM MADHA TEFKIDUNE
  12,72,KALU NEFKIDU SUWA’AL-MELIKI WE LIMEN XHA’E BIHI HIMLU BA’IRIN WE ‘ENA BIHI ZA’IMUN
  12,73,KALU TE-ELLAHI LEKAD ‘ALIMTUM MA XHI’NA LINUFSIDE FIL-’ERDI WE MA KUNNA SARIKINE
  12,74,KALU FEMA XHEZA’UUHU ‘IN KUNTUM KADHIBINE
  12,75,KALU XHEZA’UUHU MEN WUXHIDE FI REHLIHI FEHUWE XHEZA’UUHU KEDHALIKE NEXHZI EDH-DHALIMINE
  12,76,FEBEDE’E BI’EW’IJETIHIM KABLE WI’A’I ‘EHIHI THUMME ESTEHREXHEHA MIN WI’A’I ‘EHIHI KEDHALIKE KIDNA LIJUSUFE MA KANE LIJE’HUDHE ‘EHAHU FI DINIL-MELIKI ‘ILLA ‘EN JESHA’EL-LAHU NERFA’U DEREXHATIN MEN NESHA’U WE FEWKA KULLI DHI ‘ILMIN ‘ALIMUN
  12,77,KALU ‘IN JESRIK FEKAD SEREKA ‘EHUN LEHU MIN KABLU FE’ESERREHA JUSUFU FI NEFSIHI WE LEM JUBDIHA LEHUM KALE ‘ENTUM SHERRUN MEKANÆN WEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA TESIFUNE
  12,78,KALU JA ‘EJJUHAL-’AZIZU ‘INNE LEHU ‘EBÆN SHEJHÆN KEBIRÆN FEHUDH ‘EHEDENA MEKANEHU ‘INNA NERAKE MINEL-MUHSININE
  12,79,KALE MA’ADHEL-LAHI ‘EN NE’HUDHE ‘ILLA MEN WEXHEDNA META’ANA ‘INDEHU ‘INNA ‘IDHÆN LEDHALIMUNE
  12,80,FELEMMA ESTEJ’ESU MINHU HALESU NEXHIJÆN KALE KEBIRUHUM ‘ELEM TA’LEMU ‘ENNE ‘EBAKUM KAD ‘EHADHE ‘ALEJKUM MEWTHIKÆN MINEL-LAHI WE MIN KABLU MA FERRETTUM FI JUSUFE FELEN ‘EBREHEL-’ERDE HETTA JE’DHENE LI ‘EBI ‘EW JEHKUMEL-LAHU LI WE HUWE HAJRUL-HAKIMINE
  12,81,ERXHI’U ‘ILA ‘EBIKUM FEKULU JA ‘EBANA ‘INNE EBNEKE SEREKA WE MA SHEHIDNA ‘ILLA BIMA ‘ALIMNA WE MA KUNNA LILGAJBI HAFIDHINE
  12,82,WE ES’ELIL-KARJETEL-LETI KUNNA FIHA WEL-’IREL-LETI ‘EKBELNA FIHA WE ‘INNA LESADIKUNE
  12,83,KALE BEL SEWWELET LEKUM ‘ENFUSUKUM ‘EMRÆN FESEBRUN XHEMILUN ‘ASALLAHU ‘EN JE’TIJENI BIHIM XHEMI’ÆN ‘INNEHU HUWEL-’ALIMUL-HEKIMU
  12,84,WE TEWELLA ‘ANHUM WE KALE JA ‘ESEFA ‘ALA JUSUFE WE EBJEDDET ‘AJNAHU MINEL-HUZNI FEHUWE KEDHIMUN
  12,85,KALU TE-ELLAHI TEFTE’U TEDHKURU JUSUFE HETTA TEKUNE HEREDÆN ‘EW TEKUNE MINEL-HALIKINE
  12,86,KALE ‘INNEMA ‘ESHKU BETHTHI WE HUZNI ‘ILA ELLAHI WE ‘A’LEMU MINEL-LAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  12,87,JA BENIJE EDH/HEBU FETEHESSESU MIN JUSUFE WE ‘EHIHI WE LA TEJ’ESU MIN REWHI ELLAHI ‘INNEHU LA JEJ’ESU MIN REWHI ELLAHI ‘ILLAL-KAWMUL-KAFIRUNE
  12,88,FELEMMA DEHALU ‘ALEJHI KALU JA ‘EJJUHAL-’AZIZU MESSENA WE ‘EHLENA ED-DURRU WE XHI’NA BIBIDA’ATIN MUZXHÆTIN FE’EWFI LENAL-KEJLE WE TESEDDEK ‘ALEJNA ‘INNALL-LLAHE JEXHZIL-MUTESEDDIKINE
  12,89,KALE HEL ‘ALIMTUM MA FE’ALTUM BIJUSUFE WE ‘EHIHI ‘IDH ‘ENTUM XHAHILUNE
  12,90,KALU ‘E’INNEKE LE’ENTE JUSUFU KALE ‘ENA JUSUFU WE HEDHA ‘EHI KAD MENNEL-LAHU ‘ALEJNA ‘INNEHU MEN JETTEKI WE JESBIR FE’INNALL-LLAHE LA JUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MUHSININE
  12,91,KALU TE-ELLAHI LEKAD ‘ATHEREKEL-LAHU ‘ALEJNA WE ‘IN KUNNA LEHATI’INE
  12,92,KALE LA TETHRIBE ‘ALEJKUMUL-JEWME JEGFIRU ELLAHU LEKUM WE HUWE ‘ERHEMU ER-RAHIMINE
  12,93,EDH/HEBU BIKAMISI HADHA FE’ELKUHU ‘ALA WEXHHI ‘EBI JE’TI BESIRÆN WE ‘TUNI BI’EHLIKUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  12,94,WE LEMMA FESELETIL-’IRU KALE ‘EBUHUM ‘INNI LE’EXHIDU RIHE JUSUFE LEWLA ‘EN TUFENNIDUNI
  12,95,KALU TE-ELLAHI ‘INNEKE LEFI DELALIKEL-KADIMI
  12,96,FELEMMA ‘EN XHA’EL-BESHIRU ‘ELKAHU ‘ALA WEXHHIHI FARTEDDE BESIRÆN KALE ‘ELEM ‘EKUL LEKUM ‘INNI ‘A’LEMU MINEL-LAHI MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  12,97,KALU JA ‘EBANA ESTEGFIR LENA DHUNUBENA ‘INNA KUNNA HATI’INE
  12,98,KALE SEWFE ‘ESTEGFIRU LEKUM RABBI ‘INNEHU HUWEL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  12,99,FELEMMA DEHALU ‘ALA JUSUFE ‘AWA ‘ILEJHI ‘EBEWEJHI WE KALE EDHULU MISRE ‘IN SHA’EL-LAHU ‘AMININE
  12,100,WE REFE’A ‘EBEWEJHI ‘ALEL-’ARSHI WE HARRU LEHU SUXHXHEDÆN WE KALE JA ‘EBETI HADHA TE’WILU RU’UJA J MIN KABLU KAD XHE’ALEHA RABBI HEKKÆN WE KAD ‘EHSENE BI ‘IDH ‘EHREXHENI MINE ES-SIXHNI WE XHA’E BIKUM MINEL-BEDWI MIN BA’DI ‘EN NEZEGA ESH-SHEJTANU BEJNI WE
  12,101,REBBI KAD ‘ATEJTENI MINEL-MULKI WE ‘ALLEMTENI MIN TE’WILIL-’EHADITHI FATIRE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘ENTE WE LIJI FI ED-DUNJA WEL-’AHIRETI TEWEFFENI MUSLIMÆN WE ‘ELHIKNI BIS-SALIHINE
  12,102,DHALIKE MIN ‘ENBA’IL-GAJBI NUHIHI ‘ILEJKE WE MA KUNTE LEDEJHIM ‘IDH ‘EXHMA’U ‘EMREHUM WE HUM JEMKURUNE
  12,103,WE MA ‘EKTHERU EN-NASI WE LEW HERESTE BIMU’UMININE
  12,104,WE MA TES’ELUHUM ‘ALEJHI MIN ‘EXHRIN ‘IN HUWE ‘ILLA DHIKRUN LIL’ALEMINE
  12,105,WE KE’EJJIN MIN ‘AJETIN FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI JEMURRUNE ‘ALEJHA WE HUM ‘ANHA MU’RIDUNE
  12,106,WE MA JU’UMINU ‘EKTHERUHUM BILLAHI ‘ILLA WE HUM MUSHRIKUNE
  12,107,‘EFE’EMINU ‘EN TE’TIJEHUM GASHIJETUN MIN ‘ADHABI ELLAHI ‘EW TE’TIJEHUMU ES-SA’ATU BEGTETEN WE HUM LA JESH’URUNE
  12,108,KUL HEDHIHI SEBILI ‘ED’U ‘ILA ELLAHI ‘ALA BESIRETIN ‘ENA WE MENI ETTEBE’ANI WE SUBHANEL-LAHI WE MA ‘ENA MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  12,109,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE ‘ILLA RIXHALÆN NUHI ‘ILEJHIM MIN ‘EHLIL-KURA ‘EFELEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE LEDARUL-’AHIRETI HAJRUN LILLEDHINE ETTEKAW ‘EFELA TA’KILUNE
  12,110,HETTA ‘IDHA ESTEJ’ESE ER-RUSULU WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHUM KAD KUDHIBU XHA’EHUM NESRUNA FENUXHXHIJE MEN NESHA’U WE LA JUREDDU BE’SUNA ‘ANIL-KAWMIL-MUXHRIMINE
  12,111,LEKAD KANE FI KASESIHIM ‘IBRETUN LI’WLIL-’ELBABI MA KANE HEDITHÆN JUFTERA WE LEKIN TESDIKAL-LEDHI BEJNE JEDEJHI WE TEFSILE KULLI SHEJ’IN WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  13,1,‘ELIF-LAM-MIM-RA TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABI WEL-LEDHI ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE MIN RABBIKEL-HEKKU WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JU’UMINUNE
  13,2,ELLAHUL-LEDHI REFE’A ES-SEMAWATI BIGAJRI ‘AMEDIN TEREWNEHA THUMME ESTEWA ‘ALEL-’ARSHI WE SEHHARE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE KULLUN JEXHRI LI’XHELIN MUSEMMEN JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE JUFESSILUL-’AJATI LE’ALLEKUM BILIKA’I RABBIKUM TUKINUNE
  13,3,WE HUWEL-LEDHI MEDDEL-’ERDE WE XHE’ALE FIHA REWASIJE WE ‘ENHARÆN WE MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI XHE’ALE FIHA ZEWXHEJNI ETHNEJNI JUGSHIL-LEJLE EN-NEHARE ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  13,4,WE FIL-’ERDI KITA’UN MUTEXHAWIRATUN WE XHENNATUN MIN ‘A’NABIN WE ZER’UN WE NEHILUN SINWANUN WE GAJRU SINWANIN JUSKA BIMA’IN WAHIDIN WE NUFEDDILU BA’DEHA ‘ALA BA’DIN FIL-’UKULI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  13,5,WE ‘IN TA’XHEB FE’AXHEBUN KAWLUHUM ‘E’IDHA KUNNA TURABÆN ‘E’INNA LEFI HALKIN XHEDIDIN ‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIREBBIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKEL-’EGLALU FI ‘A’NAKIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  13,6,WE JESTA’XHILUNEKE BIS-SEJJI’ETI KABLEL-HESENETI WE KAD HALET MIN KABLIHIMUL-METHULATU WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEDHU MEGFIRETIN LILNNASI ‘ALA DHULMIHIM WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LESHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  13,7,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE MUNDHIRUN WE LIKULLI KAWMIN HADIN
  13,8,ELLAHU JA’LEMU MA TEHMILU KULLU ‘UNTHA WE MA TEGIDUL-’ERHAMU WE MA TEZDADU WE KULLU SHEJ’IN ‘INDEHU BIMIKDARIN
  13,9,‘ALIMUL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETIL-KEBIRUL-MUTA’ALI
  13,10,SEWA’UN MINKUM MEN ‘ESERREL-KAWLE WE MEN XHEHERE BIHI WE MEN HUWE MUSTEHFIN BIL-LEJLI WE SARIBUN BIN-NEHARI
  13,11,LEHU MU’AKKIBATUN MIN BEJNI JEDEJHI WE MIN HALFIHI JEHFEDHUNEHU MIN ‘EMRI ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JUGAJJIRU MA BIKAWMIN HETTA JUGAJJIRU MA BI’ENFUSIHIM WE ‘IDHA ‘ERADEL-LAHU BIKAWMIN SU’ÆN FELA MEREDDE LEHU WE MA LEHUM MIN DUNIHI MIN WE E
  13,12,HUWEL-LEDHI JURIKUMUL-BERKA HAWFÆN WE TEMA’ÆN WE JUNSHI’U ES-SEHABE ETH-THIKALE
  13,13,WE JUSEBBIHU ER-RA’DU BIHEMDIHI WEL-MELA’IKETU MIN HIFETIHI WE JURSILU ES-SEWA’IKA FEJUSIBU BIHA MEN JESHA’U WE HUM JUXHADILUNE FI ELLAHI WE HUWE SHEDIDUL-MIHALI
  13,14,LEHU DA’WETUL-HEKKI WEL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNIHI LA JESTEXHIBUNE LEHUM BISHEJ’IN ‘ILLA KEBASITI KEFFEJHI ‘ILAL-MA’I LIJEBLUGA FAHU WE MA HUWE BIBALIGIHI WE MA DU’A’UL-KAFIRINE ‘ILLA FI DELALIN
  13,15,WE LILLEHI JESXHUDU MEN FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI TEW’ÆN WE KERHÆN WE DHILALUHUM BIL-GUDUWI WEL-’ASALI
  13,16,KUL MEN REBBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI KULI ELLAHU KUL ‘EFATTEHADHTUM MIN DUNIHI ‘EWLIJA’E LA JEMLIKUNE LI’NFUSIHIM NEF’ÆN WE LA DERRÆN KUL HEL JESTEWIL-’A’MA WEL-BESIRU ‘EM HEL TESTEWI EDH-DHULUMATU WE EN-NUR ‘EM XHE’ALU LILLAHI SHUREKA’E HALEKU KEHALKIHI F
  13,17,‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FESALET ‘EWDIJETUN BIKADERIHA FAHTEMELE ES-SEJLU ZEBEDÆN RABIÆN WE MIMMA JUKIDUNE ‘ALEJHI FI EN-NARI EBTIGA’E HILJETIN ‘EW META’IN ZEBEDUN MITHLUHU KEDHALIKE JEDRIBU ELLAHUL-HEKKA WEL-BATILE FE’EMMA EZ-ZEBEDU FEJEDH/HEBU XHUFA
  13,18,LILLEDHINE ESTEXHABU LIREBBIHIMUL-HUSNA WEL-LEDHINE LEM JESTEXHIBU LEHU LEW ‘ENNE LEHUM MA FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN WE MITHLEHU ME’AHU LAFTEDEW BIHI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM SU’UL-HISABI WE ME’WAHUM XHEHENNEMU WE BI’SEL-MIHADU
  13,19,‘EFEMEN JA’LEMU ‘ENNEMA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE MIN RABBIKEL-HEKKU KEMEN HUWE ‘A’MA ‘INNEMA JETEDHEKKERU ‘ULUL-’ELBABI
  13,20,EL-LEDHINE JUFUNE BI’AHDI ELLAHI WE LA JENKUDUNEL-MITHAKA
  13,21,WEL-LEDHINE JESILUNE MA ‘EMEREL-LAHU BIHI ‘EN JUSELE WE JEHSHEWNE REBBEHUM WE JEHAFUNE SU’EL-HISABI
  13,22,WEL-LEDHINE SEBERU EBTIGA’E WEXHHI RABBIHIM WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ENFEKU MIMMA REZEKNAHUM SIRRÆN WE ‘ALANIJETEN WE JEDRE’UNE BIL-HESENETI ES-SEJJI’ETE ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘UKBA ED-DARI
  13,23,XHENNATU ‘ADNIN JEDHULUNEHA WE MEN SELEHE MIN ‘ABA’IHIM WE ‘EZWAXHIHIM WE DHURRIJATIHIM WEL-MELA’IKETU JEDHULUNE ‘ALEJHIM MIN KULLI BABIN
  13,24,SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUM BIMA SEBERTUM FENI’ME ‘UKBA ED-DARI
  13,25,WEL-LEDHINE JENKUDUNE ‘AHDEL-LAHI MIN BA’DI MITHAKIHI WE JEKTA’UNE MA ‘EMEREL-LAHU BIHI ‘EN JUSELE WE JUFSIDUNE FIL-’ERDI ‘ULA’IKE LEHUMUL-LA’NETU WE LEHUM SU’U ED-DARI
  13,26,ELLAHU JEBSUTU ER-RIZKA LIMEN JESHA’U WE JEKDIRU WE FERIHU BIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE MAL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA FIL-’AHIRETI ‘ILLA META’UN
  13,27,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEWLA ‘UNZILE ‘ALEJHI ‘AJETUN MIN RABBIHI KUL ‘INNALL-LLAHE JUDILLU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI ‘ILEJHI MEN ‘ENABE
  13,28,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE TETME’INNU KULUBUHUM BIDHIKRI ELLAHI ‘ELA BIDHIKRI ELLAHI TETME’INNUL-KULUBU
  13,29,EL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI TUBA LEHUM WE HUSNU ME’ABIN
  13,30,KEDHALIKE ‘ERSELNAKE FI ‘UMMETIN KAD HALET MIN KABLIHA ‘UMEMUN LITETLUWE ‘ALEJHIMUL-LEDHI ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE WE HUM JEKFURUNE BIR-REHMENI KUL HUWE RABBI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE ‘ALEJHI TEWEKKELTU WE ‘ILEJHI METABI
  13,31,WE LEW ‘ENNE KUR’ANÆN SUJJIRET BIHIL-XHIBALU ‘EW KUTTI’AT BIHIL-’ERDU ‘EW KULLIME BIHIL-MEWTA BEL LILLAHIL-’EMRU XHEMI’ÆN ‘EFELEM JEJ’ESIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘EN LEW JESHA’U ELLAHU LEHEDA EN-NASE XHEMI’ÆN WE LA JEZALUL-LEDHINE KEFERU TUSIBUHUM BIMA SENA’U KAR
  13,32,WE LEKADI ESTUHZI’E BIRUSULIN MIN KABLIKE FE’EMLEJTU LILLEDHINE KEFERU THUMME ‘EHADHTUHUM FEKEJFE KANE ‘IKABI
  13,33,‘EFEMEN HUWE KA’IMUN ‘ALA KULLI NEFSIN BIMA KESEBET WE XHE’ALU LILLAHI SHUREKA’E KUL SEMMUHUM ‘EM TUNEBBI’UNEHU BIMA LA JA’LEMU FIL-’ERDI ‘EM BIDHAHIRIN MINEL-KAWLI BEL ZUJJINE LILLEDHINE KEFERU MEKRUHUM WE SUDDU ‘ANI ES-SEBILI WE MEN JUDLILI ELLAHU FEMA
  13,34,LEHUM ‘ADHABUN FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE LE’ADHABUL-’AHIRETI ‘ESHEKKU WE MA LEHUM MINEL-LAHI MIN WAKIN
  13,35,METHELUL-XHENNETI ELLETI WU’IDEL-MUTTEKUNE TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU ‘UKULUHA DA’IMUN WE DHILLUHA TILKE ‘UKBAL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW WE ‘UKBAL-KAFIRINE EN-NARU
  13,36,WEL-LEDHINE ‘ATEJNAHUMUL-KITABE JEFREHUNE BIMA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKE WE MINEL-’EHZABI MEN JUNKIRU BA’DEHU KUL ‘INNEMA ‘UMIRTU ‘EN ‘A’BUDEL-LAHE WE LA ‘USHRIKE BIHI ‘ILEJHI ‘ED’U WE ‘ILEJHI ME’ABI
  13,37,WE KEDHELIKE ‘ENZELNAHU HUKMÆN ‘AREBIJÆN WE LE’INI ETTEBA’TE ‘EHWA’EHUM BA’DEMA XHA’EKE MINEL-’ILMI MA LEKE MINEL-LAHI MIN WE LIJIN WE LA WAKIN
  13,38,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA RUSULÆN MIN KABLIKE WE XHE’ALNA LEHUM ‘EZWAXHÆN WE DHURRIJETEN WE MA KANE LIRESULIN ‘EN JE’TIJE BI’AJETIN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI LIKULLI ‘EXHELIN KITABUN
  13,39,JEMHU ELLAHU MA JESHA’U WE JUTHBITU WE ‘INDEHU ‘UMMUL-KITABI
  13,40,WE ‘IN MA NURIJENNEKE BA’DEL-LEDHI NA’IDUHUM ‘EW NETEWEFFEJENNEKE FE’INNEMA ‘ALEJKEL-BELAGU WE ‘ALEJNAL-HISABU
  13,41,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ENNA NE’TIL-’ERDE NENKUSUHA MIN ‘ETRAFIHA WEL-LAHU JEHKUMU LA MU’AKKIBE LIHUKMIHI WE HUWE SERI’UL-HISABI
  13,42,WE KAD MEKEREL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FELILLAHIL-MEKRU XHEMI’ÆN JA’LEMU MA TEKSIBU KULLU NEFSIN WE SEJA’LEMUL-KUFFARU LIMEN ‘UKBA ED-DARI
  13,43,WE JEKULUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LESTE MURSELÆN KUL KEFA BILLAHI SHEHIDÆN BEJNI WE BEJNEKUM WE MEN ‘INDEHU ‘ILMUL-KITABI
  14,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA KITABUN ‘ENZELNAHU ‘ILEJKE LITUHRIXHE EN-NASE MINE EDH-DHULUMATI ‘ILA EN-NUR BI’IDHNI RABBIHIM ‘ILA SIRATIL-’AZIZIL-HEMIDI
  14,2,ELLAHIL-LEDHI LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE WEJLUN LILKAFIRINE MIN ‘ADHABIN SHEDIDIN
  14,3,EL-LEDHINE JESTEHIBBUNEL-HEJÆTE ED-DUNJA ‘ALEL-’AHIRETI WE JESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE JEBGUNEHA ‘IWEXHÆN ‘ULA’IKE FI DELALIN BA’IDIN
  14,4,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN RESULIN ‘ILLA BILISANI KAWMIHI LIJUBEJJINE LEHUM FEJUDILLU ELLAHU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  14,5,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA MUSA BI’AJATINA ‘EN ‘EHRIXH KAWMEKE MINE EDH-DHULUMATI ‘ILA EN-NURI WE DHEKKIRHUM BI’EJJAMI ELLAHI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKULLI SEBBARIN SHEKURIN
  14,6,WE ‘IDH KALE MUSA LIKAWMIHI EDHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘ALEJKUM ‘IDH ‘ENXHAKUM MIN ‘ALI FIR’AWNE JESUMUNEKUM SU’EL-’ADHABI WE JUDHEBBIHUNE ‘EBNA’EKUM WE JESTEHJUNE NISA’EKUM WE FI DHALIKUM BELA’UN MIN RABBIKUM ‘ADHIMUN
  14,7,WE ‘IDH TE’EDHDHENE REBBUKUM LE’IN SHEKERTUM LE’EZIDENNEKUM WE LE’IN KEFERTUM ‘INNE ‘ADHABI LESHEDIDUN
  14,8,WE KALE MUSA ‘IN TEKFURU ‘ENTUM WE MEN FIL-’ERDI XHEMI’ÆN FE’INNALL-LLAHE LEGANIJUN HEMIDUN
  14,9,‘ELEM JE’TIKUM NEBE’UL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIKUM KAWMI NUHIN WE ‘ADIN WE THEMUDE WEL-LEDHINE MIN BA’DIHIM LA JA’LEMUHUM ‘ILLALLAHU XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FEREDDU ‘EJDIJEHUM FI ‘EFWAHIHIM WE KALU ‘INNA KEFERNA BIMA ‘URSILTUM BIHI WE ‘INNA LEFI SHEKK
  14,10,KALET RUSULUHUM ‘EFI ELLAHI SHEKKUN FATIRI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI JED’UKUM LIJEGFIRE LEKUM MIN DHUNUBIKUM WE JU’UEHHIREKUM ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN KALU ‘IN ‘ENTUM ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUNA TURIDUNE ‘EN TESUDDUNA ‘AMMA KANE JA’BUDU ‘ABA’UUNA FE’TUNA BISULTANIN
  14,11,KALET LEHUM RUSULUHUM ‘IN NEHNU ‘ILLA BESHERUN MITHLUKUM WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JEMUNNU ‘ALA MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI WE MA KANE LENA ‘EN NE’TIJEKUM BISULTANIN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MU’UMINUNE
  14,12,WE MA LENA ‘ELLA NETEWEKKELE ‘ALA ELLAHI WE KAD HEDANA SUBULENA WE LENESBIRENNE ‘ALA MA ‘ADHEJTUMUNA WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MUTEWEKKILUNE
  14,13,WE KALEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LIRUSULIHIM LENUHRIXHENNEKUM MIN ‘ERDINA ‘EW LETA’UDUNNE FI MILLETINA FE’EWHA ‘ILEJHIM REBBUHUM LENUHLIKENNE EDH-DHALIMINE
  14,14,WE LENUSKINENNEKUMUL-’ERDE MIN BA’DIHIM DHALIKE LIMEN HAFE MEKAMI WE HAFE WA’IDI
  14,15,WE ESTEFTEHU WE HABE KULLU XHEBBARIN ‘ANIDIN
  14,16,MIN WERA’IHI XHEHENNEMU WE JUSKA MIN MA’IN SEDIDIN
  14,17,JETEXHERRA’UHU WE LA JEKADU JUSIGUHU WE JE’TIHIL-MEWTU MIN KULLI MEKANIN WE MA HUWE BIMEJJITIN WE MIN WERA’IHI ‘ADHABUN GALIDHUN
  14,18,METHELUL-LEDHINE KEFERU BIREBBIHIM ‘A’MALUHUM KEREMADIN ESHTEDDET BIHI ER-RIHU FI JEWMIN ‘ASIFIN LA JEKDIRUNE MIMMA KESEBU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN DHALIKE HUWE ED-DELALUL-BA’IDU
  14,19,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI ‘IN JESHE’ JUDH/HIBKUM WE JE’TI BIHALKIN XHEDIDIN
  14,20,WE MA DHALIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI BI’AZIZIN
  14,21,WE BEREZU LILLAHI XHEMI’ÆN FEKALE ED-DU’AFA’U LILLEDHINE ESTEKBERU ‘INNA KUNNA LEKUM TEBA’ÆN FEHEL ‘ENTUM MUGNUNE ‘ANNA MIN ‘ADHABI ELLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN KALU LEW HEDANALLAHU LEHEDEJNAKUM SEWA’UN ‘ALEJNA ‘EXHEZI’NA ‘EM SEBERNA MA LENA MIN MEHISIN
  14,22,WE KALE ESH-SHEJTANU LEMMA KUDIJEL-’EMRU ‘INNALL-LLAHE WE’ADEKUM WA’DEL-HEKKI WE WE’ADTUKUM FE’EHLEFTUKUM WE MA KANE LI ‘ALEJKUM MIN SULTANIN ‘ILLA ‘EN DE’AWTUKUM FASTEXHEBTUM LI FELA TELUMUNI WE LUMU ‘ENFUSEKUM MA ‘ENA BIMUSRIHIKUM WE MA ‘ENTUM BIMUSRIHI
  14,23,WE ‘UDHILEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA BI’IDHNI RABBIHIM TEHIJETUHUM FIHA SELAMUN
  14,24,‘ELEM TERA KEJFE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN KELIMETEN TEJJIBETEN KESHEXHERETIN TEJJIBETIN ‘ESLUHA THABITUN WE FER’UHA FI ES-SEMA’I
  14,25,TU’UTI ‘UKULEHA KULLE HININ BI’IDHNI RABBIHA WE JEDRIBU ELLAHUL-’EMTHALE LILNNASI LE’ALLEHUM JETEDHEKKERUNE
  14,26,WE METHELU KELIMETIN HABITHETIN KESHEXHERETIN HABITHETIN EXHTUTHTHET MIN FEWKIL-’ERDI MA LEHA MIN KARARIN
  14,27,JUTHEBBITU ELLAHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU BIL-KAWLI ETH-THABITI FIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA WE FIL-’AHIRETI WE JUDILLU ELLAHU EDH-DHALIMINE WE JEF’ALU ELLAHU MA JESHA’U
  14,28,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILAL-LEDHINE BEDDELU NI’METEL-LAHI KUFRÆN WE ‘EHELLU KAWMEHUM DAREL-BEWARI
  14,29,XHEHENNEME JESLEWNEHA WE BI’SEL-KARARU
  14,30,WE XHE’ALU LILLAHI ‘ENDADÆN LIJUDILLU ‘AN SEBILIHI KUL TEMETTA’U FE’INNE MESIREKUM ‘ILA EN-NARI
  14,31,KUL LI’IBADIJEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU JUKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE JUNFIKU MIMMA REZEKNAHUM SIRRÆN WE ‘ALANIJETEN MIN KABLI ‘EN JE’TIJE JEWMUN LA BEJ’UN FIHI WE LA HILALUN
  14,32,ELLAHUL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHREXHE BIHI MINE ETH-THEMERATI RIZKÆN LEKUM WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-FULKE LITEXHRIJE FIL-BEHRI BI’EMRIHI WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-’ENHARE
  14,33,WE SEHHARE LEKUMU ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE DA’IBEJNI WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHAR
  14,34,WE ‘ATAKUM MIN KULLI MA SE’ELTUMUHU WE ‘IN TA’UDDU NI’METEL-LAHI LA TUHSUHA ‘INNEL-’INSANE LEDHELUMUN KEFFARUN
  14,35,WE ‘IDH KALE ‘IBRAHIMU RABBI EXH’AL HADHAL-BELEDE ‘AMINÆN WE EXHNUBNI WE BENIJE ‘EN NA’BUDEL-’ESNAME
  14,36,REBBI ‘INNEHUNNE ‘EDLELNE KETHIRÆN MINE EN-NASI FEMEN TEBI’ANI FE’INNEHU MINNI WE MEN ‘ASANI FE’INNEKE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  14,37,REBBENA ‘INNI ‘ESKENTU MIN DHURRIJETI BIWADIN GAJRI DHI ZER’IN ‘INDE BEJTIKEL-MUHERREMI REBBENA LIJUKIMU ES-SELÆTE FAXH’AL ‘EF’IDETEN MINE EN-NASI TEHWI ‘ILEJHIM WE ERZUKHUM MINE ETH-THEMERATI LE’ALLEHUM JESHKURUNE
  14,38,REBBENA ‘INNEKE TA’LEMU MA NUHFI WE MA NU’LINU WE MA JEHFA ‘ALA ELLAHI MIN SHEJ’IN FIL-’ERDI WE LA FI ES-SEMA’I
  14,39,EL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI WEHEBE LI ‘ALEL-KIBERI ‘ISMA’ILE WE ‘ISHAKA ‘INNE RABBI LESEMI’U ED-DU’A’I
  14,40,REBBI EXH’ALNI MUKIME ES-SELÆTI WE MIN DHURRIJETI REBBENA WE TEKABBEL DU’A’I
  14,41,REBBENA EGFIR LI WE LIWALIDEJJE WE LILMU’UMININE JEWME JEKUMUL-HISABU
  14,42,WE LA TEHSEBENNEL-LAHE GAFILÆN ‘AMMA JA’MELU EDH-DHALIMUNE ‘INNEMA JU’UEHHIRUHUM LIJEWMIN TESHHASU FIHIL-’EBSARU
  14,43,MUHTI’INE MUKNI’I RU’USIHIM LA JERTEDDU ‘ILEJHIM TERFUHUM WE ‘EF’IDETUHUM HEWA’UN
  14,44,WE ‘ENDHIRI EN-NASE JEWME JE’TIHIMUL-’ADHABU FEJEKULUL-LEDHINE DHELEMU REBBENA ‘EHHIRNA ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN KARIBIN NUXHIB DA’WETEKE WE NETTEBI’I ER-RUSULE ‘EWELEM TEKUNU ‘EKSEMTUM MIN KABLU MA LEKUM MIN ZEWALIN
  14,45,WE SEKENTUM FI MESAKINIL-LEDHINE DHELEMU ‘ENFUSEHUM WE TEBEJJENE LEKUM KEJFE FE’ALNA BIHIM WE DEREBNA LEKUMUL-’EMTHALE
  14,46,WE KAD MEKERU MEKREHUM WE ‘INDEL-LAHI MEKRUHUM WE ‘IN KANE MEKRUHUM LITEZULE MINHUL-XHIBALU
  14,47,FELA TEHSEBENNEL-LAHE MUHLIFE WA’DIHI RUSULEHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN DHU ENTIKAMIN
  14,48,JEWME TUBEDDELUL-’ERDU GAJREL-’ERDI WE ES-SEMAWATU WE BEREZU LILLAHIL-WAHIDIL-KAHHARI
  14,49,WE TERAL-MUXHRIMINE JEWME’IDHIN MUKARRENINE FIL-’ESFADI
  14,50,SERABILUHUM MIN KATIRANIN WE TEGSHA WUXHUHEHUMU EN-NARU
  14,51,LIJEXHZIJEL-LAHU KULLE NEFSIN MA KESEBET ‘INNALL-LLAHE SERI’UL-HISABI
  14,52,HADHA BELAGUN LILNNASI WE LIJUNDHERU BIHI WE LIJA’LEMU ‘ENNEMA HUWE ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN WE LIJEDHDHEKKERE ‘ULUL-’ELBABI
  15,1,‘ELIF-LAM-RA TILKE ‘AJATUL-KITABI WE KUR’ANIN MUBININ
  15,2,RUBEMA JEWEDDUL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEW KANU MUSLIMINE
  15,3,DHERHUM JE’KULU WE JETEMETTA’U WE JULHIHIMUL-’EMELU FESEWFE JA’LEMUNE
  15,4,WE MA ‘EHLEKNA MIN KARJETIN ‘ILLA WE LEHA KITABUN MA’LUMUN
  15,5,MA TESBIKU MIN ‘UMMETIN ‘EXHELEHA WE MA JESTE’HIRUNE
  15,6,WE KALU JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHI NUZZILE ‘ALEJHI EDH-DHIKRU ‘INNEKE LEMEXHNUNUN
  15,7,LEW MA TE’TINA BIL-MELA’IKETI ‘IN KUNTE MINE ES-SADIKINE
  15,8,MA NUNEZZILUL-MELA’IKETE ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI WE MA KANU ‘IDHÆN MUNDHERINE
  15,9,‘INNA NEHNU NEZZELNA EDH-DHIKRE WE ‘INNA LEHU LEHAFIDHUNE
  15,10,WE LEKAD ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE FI SHIJA’IL-’EWWELINE
  15,11,WE MA JE’TIHIM MIN RESULIN ‘ILLA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UNE
  15,12,KEDHALIKE NESLUKUHU FI KULUBIL-MUXHRIMINE
  15,13,LA JU’UMINUNE BIHI WE KAD HALET SUNNETUL-’EWWELINE
  15,14,WE LEW FETEHNA ‘ALEJHIM BABÆN MINE ES-SEMA’I FEDHELLU FIHI JA’RUXHUNE
  15,15,LEKALU ‘INNEMA SUKKIRET ‘EBSARUNA BEL NEHNU KAWMUN MESHURUNE
  15,16,WE LEKAD XHE’ALNA FI ES-SEMA’I BURUXHÆN WE ZEJJENNAHA LILNNADHIRINE
  15,17,WE HEFIDHNAHA MIN KULLI SHEJTANIN REXHIMIN
  15,18,‘ILLA MENI ESTEREKA ES-SEM’A FE’ETBE’AHU SHIHABUN MUBINUN
  15,19,WEL-’ERDE MEDEDNAHA WE ‘ELKAJNA FIHA REWASIJE WE ‘ENBETNA FIHA MIN KULLI SHEJ’IN MEWZUNIN
  15,20,WE XHE’ALNA LEKUM FIHA MA’AJISHE WE MEN LESTUM LEHU BIRAZIKINE
  15,21,WE ‘IN MIN SHEJ’IN ‘ILLA ‘INDENA HAZA’INUHU WE MA NUNEZZILUHU ‘ILLA BIKADERIN MA’LUMIN
  15,22,WE ‘ERSELNA ER-RIJAHE LEWAKIHE FE’ENZELNA MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’ESKAJNAKUMUHU WE MA ‘ENTUM LEHU BIHAZININE
  15,23,WE ‘INNA LENEHNU NUHJI WE NUMITU WE NEHNUL-WARITHUNE
  15,24,WE LEKAD ‘ALIMNAL-MUSTEKDIMINE MINKUM WE LEKAD ‘ALIMNAL-MUSTE’HIRINE
  15,25,WE ‘INNE REBBEKE HUWE JEHSHURUHUM ‘INNEHU HEKIMUN ‘ALIMUN
  15,26,WE LEKAD HALEKNAL-’INSANE MIN SELSALIN MIN HEME’IIN MESNUNIN
  15,27,WEL-XHANNE HALEKNAHU MIN KABLU MIN NARI ES-SEMUMI
  15,28,WE ‘IDH KALE REBBUKE LILMELA’IKETI ‘INNI HALIKUN BESHERÆN MIN SELSALIN MIN HEME’IIN MESNUNIN
  15,29,FE’IDHA SEWWEJTUHU WE NEFEHTU FIHI MIN RUHI FEKA’U LEHU SAXHIDINE
  15,30,FESEXHEDEL-MELA’IKETU KULLUHUM ‘EXHMA’UNE
  15,31,‘ILLA ‘IBLISE ‘EBA ‘EN JEKUNE ME’A ES-SAXHIDINE
  15,32,KALE JA ‘IBLISU MA LEKE ‘ELLA TEKUNE ME’A ES-SAXHIDINE
  15,33,KALE LEM ‘EKUN LI’SXHUDE LIBESHERIN HALEKTEHU MIN SELSALIN MIN HEME’IIN MESNUNIN
  15,34,KALE FAHRUXH MINHA FE’INNEKE REXHIMUN
  15,35,WE ‘INNE ‘ALEJKEL-LA’NETE ‘ILA JEWMI ED-DINI
  15,36,KALE RABBI FE’ENDHIRNI ‘ILA JEWMI JUB’ATHUNE
  15,37,KALE FE’INNEKE MINEL-MUNDHERINE
  15,38,‘ILA JEWMIL-WEKTIL-MA’LUMI
  15,39,KALE RABBI BIMA ‘EGWEJTENI LE’UZEJJINENNE LEHUM FIL-’ERDI WE LE’UGWIJENNEHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  15,40,‘ILLA ‘IBADEKE MINHUMUL-MUHLESINE
  15,41,KALE HADHA SIRATUN ‘ALEJJE MUSTEKIMUN
  15,42,‘INNE ‘IBADI LEJSE LEKE ‘ALEJHIM SULTANUN ‘ILLA MENI ETTEBE’AKE MINEL-GAWINE
  15,43,WE ‘INNE XHEHENNEME LEMEW’IDUHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  15,44,LEHA SEB’ATU ‘EBWABIN LIKULLI BABIN MINHUM XHUZ’UN MEKSUMUN
  15,45,‘INNEL-MUTTEKINE FI XHENNATIN WE ‘UJUNIN
  15,46,EDHULUHA BISELAMIN ‘AMININE
  15,47,WE NEZA’NA MA FI SUDURIHIM MIN GILLIN ‘IHWANÆN ‘ALA SURURIN MUTEKABILINE
  15,48,LA JEMESSUHUM FIHA NESEBUN WE MA HUM MINHA BIMUHREXHINE
  15,49,NEBBI’ ‘IBADI ‘ENNI ‘ENAL-GAFURU ER-REHIMU
  15,50,WE ‘ENNE ‘ADHABI HUWEL-’ADHABUL-’ELIMU
  15,51,WE NEBBI’HUM ‘AN DEJFI ‘IBRAHIME
  15,52,‘IDH DEHALU ‘ALEJHI FEKALU SELAMÆN KALE ‘INNA MINKUM WEXHILUNE
  15,53,KALU LA TEWXHEL ‘INNA NUBESHSHIRUKE BIGULAMIN ‘ALIMIN
  15,54,KALE ‘EBESHSHERTUMUNI ‘ALA ‘EN MESSENIJEL-KIBERU FEBIME TUBESHSHIRUNE
  15,55,KALU BESHSHERNAKE BIL-HEKKI FELA TEKUN MINEL-KANITINE
  15,56,KALE WE MEN JEKNETU MIN REHMETI RABBIHI ‘ILLA ED-DALLUNE
  15,57,KALE FEMA HATBUKUM ‘EJJUHAL-MURSELUNE
  15,58,KALU ‘INNA ‘URSILNA ‘ILA KAWMIN MUXHRIMINE
  15,59,‘ILLA ‘ALE LUTIN ‘INNA LEMUNEXHXHUHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  15,60,‘ILLA EMRE’ETEHU KADDERNA ‘INNEHA LEMINEL-GABIRINE
  15,61,FELEMMA XHA’E ‘ALE LUTINL-MURSELUNE
  15,62,KALE ‘INNEKUM KAWMUN MUNKERUNE
  15,63,KALU BEL XHI’NAKE BIMA KANU FIHI JEMTERUNE
  15,64,WE ‘ETEJNAKE BIL-HEKKI WE ‘INNA LESADIKUNE
  15,65,FE’ESRI BI’EHLIKE BIKIT’IN MINEL-LEJLI WE ETTEBI’ ‘EDBAREHUM WE LA JELTEFIT MINKUM ‘EHEDUN WE EMDU HEJTHU TU’UMERUNE
  15,66,WE KADEJNA ‘ILEJHI DHALIKEL-’EMRE ‘ENNE DABIRE HA’UULA’ MEKTU’UN MUSBIHINE
  15,67,WE XHA’E ‘EHLUL-MEDINETI JESTEBSHIRUNE
  15,68,KALE ‘INNE HA’UULA’ DEJFI FELA TEFDEHUNI
  15,69,WE ETTEKU ELLAHE WE LA TUHZUNI
  15,70,KALU ‘EWELEM NENHEKE ‘ANIL-’ALEMINE
  15,71,KALE HA’UULA’ BENATI ‘IN KUNTUM FA’ILINE
  15,72,LE’AMRUKE ‘INNEHUM LEFI SEKRETIHIM JA’MEHUNE
  15,73,FE’EHADHET/HUMU ES-SEJHETU MUSHRIKINE
  15,74,FEXHE’ALNA ‘ALIJEHA SAFILEHA WE ‘EMTERNA ‘ALEJHIM HIXHARETEN MIN SIXHXHILIN
  15,75,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LILMUTEWESSIMINE
  15,76,WE ‘INNEHA LEBISEBILIN MUKIMIN
  15,77,‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LILMU’UMININE
  15,78,WE ‘IN KANE ‘ESHABUL-’EJKETI LEDHALIMINE
  15,79,FANTEKAMNA MINHUM WE ‘INNEHUMA LEBI’IMAMIN MUBININ
  15,80,WE LEKAD KEDHDHEBE ‘ESHABUL-HIXHRIL-MURSELINE
  15,81,WE ‘ATEJNAHUM ‘AJATINA FEKANU ‘ANHA MU’RIDINE
  15,82,WE KANU JENHITUNE MINEL-XHIBALI BUJUTÆN ‘AMININE
  15,83,FE’EHADHET/HUMU ES-SEJHETU MUSBIHINE
  15,84,FEMA ‘EGNA ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEKSIBUNE
  15,85,WE MA HALEKNA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA ‘ILLA BIL-HEKKI WE ‘INNE ES-SA’ATE LE’ATIJETUN FASFEHI ES-SEFHEL-XHEMILE
  15,86,‘INNE REBBEKE HUWEL-HALLAKUL-’ALIMU
  15,87,WE LEKAD ‘ATEJNAKE SEB’ÆN MINEL-METHANI WEL-KUR’ANEL-’ADHIME
  15,88,LA TEMUDDENNE ‘AJNEJKE ‘ILA MA METTA’NA BIHI ‘EZWAXHÆN MINHUM WE LA TEHZEN ‘ALEJHIM WE EHFID XHENAHEKE LILMU’UMININE
  15,89,WE KUL ‘INNI ‘ENA EN-NEDHIRUL-MUBINU
  15,90,KEMA ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEL-MUKTESIMINE
  15,91,EL-LEDHINE XHE’ALUL-KUR’ANE ‘IDINE
  15,92,FEWEREBBIKE LENES’ELENNEHUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  15,93,‘AMMA KANU JA’MELUNE
  15,94,FASDA’ BIMA TU’UMERU WE ‘A’RID ‘ANIL-MUSHRIKINE
  15,95,‘INNA KEFEJNAKEL-MUSTEHZI’INE
  15,96,EL-LEDHINE JEXH’ALUNE ME’A ELLAHI ‘ILEHÆN ‘AHARE FESEWFE JA’LEMUNE
  15,97,WE LEKAD NA’LEMU ‘ENNEKE JEDIKU SEDRUKE BIMA JEKULUNE
  15,98,FESEBBIH BIHEMDI RABBIKE WE KUN MINE ES-SAXHIDINE
  15,99,WE A’BUD REBBEKE HETTA JE’TIJEKEL-JEKINU
  16,1,‘ETA ‘EMRU ELLAHI FELA TESTA’XHILUHU SUBHANEHU WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  16,2,JUNEZZILUL-MELA’IKETE BIR-RUHI MIN ‘EMRIHI ‘ALA MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI ‘EN ‘ENDHIRU ‘ENNEHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA ‘ENA FE ETTEKUNI
  16,3,HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  16,4,HALEKAL-’INSANE MIN NUTFETIN FE’IDHA HUWE HASIMUN MUBINUN
  16,5,WEL-’EN’AME HALEKAHA LEKUM FIHA DIF’UN WE MENAFI’U WE MINHA TE’KULUNE
  16,6,WE LEKUM FIHA XHEMALUN HINE TURIHUNE WE HINE TESREHUNE
  16,7,WE TEHMILU ‘ETHKALEKUM ‘ILA BELEDIN LEM TEKUNU BALIGIHI ‘ILLA BISHIKKIL-’ENFUSI ‘INNE REBBEKUM LERE’UFUN REHIMUN
  16,8,WEL-HAJLE WEL-BIGALE WEL-HEMIRE LITERKEBUHA WE ZINETEN WE JEHLUKU MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  16,9,WE ‘ALA ELLAHI KASDU ES-SEBILI WE MINHA XHA’IRUN WE LEW SHA’E LEHEDAKUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  16,10,HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN LEKUM MINHU SHERABUN WE MINHU SHEXHERUN FIHI TUSIMUNE
  16,11,JUNBITU LEKUM BIHI EZ-ZER’A WE EZ-ZEJTUNE WE EN-NEHILE WEL-’A’NABE WE MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  16,12,WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE WE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE WE EN-NUXHUMU MUSEHHARATUN BI’EMRIHI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  16,13,WE MA DHERE’E LEKUM FIL-’ERDI MUHTELIFÆN ‘ELWANUHU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JEDHDHEKKERUNE
  16,14,WE HUWEL-LEDHI SEHHAREL-BEHRE LITE’KULU MINHU LEHMÆN TERIJÆN WE TESTEHRIXHU MINHU HILJETEN TELBESUNEHA WE TERAL-FULKE MEWAHIRE FIHI WE LITEBTEGU MIN FEDLIHI WE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  16,15,WE ‘ELKA FIL-’ERDI REWASIJE ‘EN TEMIDE BIKUM WE ‘ENHARÆN WE SUBULÆN LLE’ALLEKUM TEHTEDUNE
  16,16,WE ‘ALAMATIN WE BIN-NEXHMI HUM JEHTEDUNE
  16,17,‘EFEMEN JEHLUKU KEMEN LA JEHLUKU ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  16,18,WE ‘IN TA’UDDU NI’METEL-LAHI LA TUHSUHA ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,19,WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MA TUSIRRUNE WE MA TU’LINUNE
  16,20,WEL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI LA JEHLUKUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE HUM JUHLEKUNE
  16,21,‘EMWATUN GAJRU ‘EHJA’IN WE MA JESH’URUNE ‘EJJANE JUB’ATHUNE
  16,22,‘ILEHUKUM ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN FE-EL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI KULUBUHUM MUNKIRETUN WE HUM MUSTEKBIRUNE
  16,23,LA XHEREME ‘ENNEL-LAHE JA’LEMU MA JUSIRRUNE WE MA JU’LINUNE ‘INNEHU LA JUHIBBUL-MUSTEKBIRINE
  16,24,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM MADHA ‘ENZELE REBBUKUM KALU ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE
  16,25,LIJEHMILU ‘EWZAREHUM KAMILETEN JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE MIN ‘EWZARIL-LEDHINE JUDILLUNEHUM BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN ‘ELA SA’E MA JEZIRUNE
  16,26,KAD MEKEREL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FE’ETALLAHU BUNJANEHUM MINEL-KAWA’IDI FEHARRE ‘ALEJHIMU ES-SEKFU MIN FEWKIHIM WE ‘ETAHUMUL-’ADHABU MIN HEJTHU LA JESH’URUNE
  16,27,THUMME JEWMEL-KIJAMETI JUHZIHIM WE JEKULU ‘EJNE SHUREKA’IJEL-LEDHINE KUNTUM TUSHAKKUNE FIHIM KALEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILME ‘INNEL-HIZJEL-JEWME WE ES-SU’E ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE
  16,28,EL-LEDHINE TETEWEFFAHUMUL-MELA’IKETU DHALIMI ‘ENFUSIHIM FE’ELKAW ES-SELEME MA KUNNA NA’MELU MIN SU’IN BELA ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  16,29,FADHULU ‘EBWABE XHEHENNEME HALIDINE FIHA FELEBI’SE METHWAL-MUTEKEBBIRINE
  16,30,WE KILE LILLEDHINE ETTEKAW MADHA ‘ENZELE REBBUKUM KALU HAJRÆN LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENU FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA HESENETUN WE LEDARUL-’AHIRETI HAJRUN WE LENI’ME DARUL-MUTTEKINE
  16,31,XHENNATU ‘ADNIN JEDHULUNEHA TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU LEHUM FIHA MA JESHA’UNE KEDHALIKE JEXHZI ELLAHUL-MUTTEKINE
  16,32,EL-LEDHINE TETEWEFFAHUMUL-MELA’IKETU TEJJIBINE JEKULUNE SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUMU EDHULUL-XHENNETE BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  16,33,HEL JENDHURUNE ‘ILLA ‘EN TE’TIJEHUMUL-MELA’IKETU ‘EW JE’TIJE ‘EMRU RABBIKE KEDHALIKE FE’ALEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE MA DHELEMEHUMU ELLAHU WE LEKIN KANU ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  16,34,FE’ESABEHUM SEJJI’ATU MA ‘AMILU WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  16,35,WE KALEL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU LEW SHA’EL-LAHU MA ‘ABEDNA MIN DUNIHI MIN SHEJ’IN NEHNU WE LA ‘ABA’UUNA WE LA HERREMNA MIN DUNIHI MIN SHEJ’IN KEDHALIKE FE’ALEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FEHEL ‘ALA ER-RUSULI ‘ILLAL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  16,36,WE LEKAD BE’ATHNA FI KULLI ‘UMMETIN RESULÆN ‘ENI EU’BUDU ELLAHE WE EXHTENIBUT-TAGUTE FEMINHUM MEN HEDALLAHU WE MINHUM MEN HEKKAT ‘ALEJHI ED-DELALETU FESIRU FIL-’ERDI FANDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUKEDHDHIBINE
  16,37,‘IN TEHRIS ‘ALA HUDAHUM FE’INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDI MEN JUDILLU WE MA LEHUM MIN NASIRINE
  16,38,WE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM LA JEB’ATHU ELLAHU MEN JEMUTU BELA WA’DÆN ‘ALEJHI HEKKÆN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,39,LIJUBEJJINE LEHUMUL-LEDHI JEHTELIFUNE FIHI WE LIJA’LEMEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ENNEHUM KANU KADHIBINE
  16,40,‘INNEMA KAWLUNA LISHEJ’IN ‘IDHA ‘EREDNAHU ‘EN NEKULE LEHU KUN FEJEKUNU
  16,41,WEL-LEDHINE HAXHERU FI ELLAHI MIN BA’DI MA DHULIMU LENUBEWWI’ENNEHUM FI ED-DUNJA HESENETEN WE LE’EXHRUL-’AHIRETI ‘EKBERU LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  16,42,EL-LEDHINE SEBERU WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  16,43,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE ‘ILLA RIXHALÆN NUHI ‘ILEJHIM FAS’ELU ‘EHLE EDH-DHIKRI ‘IN KUNTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  16,44,BIL-BEJJINATI WE EZ-ZUBURI WE ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKE EDH-DHIKRE LITUBEJJINE LILNNASI MA NUZZILE ‘ILEJHIM WE LE’ALLEHUM JETEFEKKERUNE
  16,45,‘EFE’EMINEL-LEDHINE MEKERU ES-SEJJI’ATI ‘EN JEHSIFEL-LAHU BIHIMUL-’ERDE ‘EW JE’TIJEHUMUL-’ADHABU MIN HEJTHU LA JESH’URUNE
  16,46,‘EW JE’HUDHEHUM FI TEKALLUBIHIM FEMA HUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  16,47,‘EW JE’HUDHEHUM ‘ALA TEHAWWUFIN FE’INNE REBBEKUM LERE’UFUN REHIMUN
  16,48,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ILA MA HALEKAL-LAHU MIN SHEJ’IN JETEFEJJE’U DHILALUHU ‘ANIL-JEMINI WE ESH-SHEMA’ILI SUXHXHEDÆN LILLAHI WE HUM DAHIRUNE
  16,49,WE LILLEHI JESXHUDU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI MIN DABBETIN WEL-MELA’IKETU WE HUM LA JESTEKBIRUNE
  16,50,JEHAFUNE REBBEHUM MIN FEWKIHIM WE JEF’ALUNE MA JU’UMERUNE
  16,51,WE KALEL-LAHU LA TETTEHIDHU ‘ILEHEJNI ETHNEJNI ‘INNEMA HUWE ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN FE’IJAJE FARHEBUNI
  16,52,WE LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE LEHU ED-DINU WE ESIBÆN ‘EFEGAJREL-LAHI TETTEKUNE
  16,53,WE MA BIKUM MIN NI’METIN FEMINEL-LAHI THUMME ‘IDHA MESSEKUMU ED-DURRU FE’ILEJHI TEXH’ERUNE
  16,54,THUMME ‘IDHA KESHEFE ED-DURRE ‘ANKUM ‘IDHA FERIKUN MINKUM BIREBBIHIM JUSHRIKUNE
  16,55,LIJEKFURU BIMA ‘ATEJNAHUM FETEMETTA’U FESEWFE TA’LEMUNE
  16,56,WE JEXH’ALUNE LIMA LA JA’LEMUNE NESIBÆN MIMMA REZEKNAHUM TE-ELLAHI LETUS’ELUNNE ‘AMMA KUNTUM TEFTERUNE
  16,57,WE JEXH’ALUNE LILLAHIL-BENATI SUBHANEHU WE LEHUM MA JESHTEHUNE
  16,58,WE ‘IDHA BUSHSHIRE ‘EHEDUHUM BIL-’UNTHA DHELLE WEXHHUHU MUSWEDDÆN WE HUWE KEDHIMUN
  16,59,JETEWARA MINEL-KAWMI MIN SU’I MA BUSHSHIRE BIHI ‘EJUMSIKUHU ‘ALA HUNIN ‘EM JEDUSSUHU FIT-TURABI ‘ELA SA’E MA JEHKUMUNE
  16,60,LILLEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI METHELU ES-SEW’I WE LILLEHIL-METHELUL-’A’LA WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  16,61,WE LEW JU’UAHIDHU ELLAHU EN-NASE BIDHULMIHIM MA TEREKE ‘ALEJHA MIN DABBETIN WE LEKIN JU’UEHHIRUHUM ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN FE’IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHUM LA JESTE’HIRUNE SA’ATEN WE LA JESTEKDIMUNE
  16,62,WE JEXH’ALUNE LILLAHI MA JEKREHUNE WE TESIFU ‘ELSINETUHUMUL-KEDHIBE ‘ENNE LEHUMUL-HUSNA LA XHEREME ‘ENNE LEHUMU EN-NARE WE ‘ENNEHUM MUFRETUNE
  16,63,TE-ELLAHI LEKAD ‘ERSELNA ‘ILA ‘UMEMIN MIN KABLIKE FEZEJJENE LEHUMU ESH-SHEJTANU ‘A’MALEHUM FEHUWE WELIJUHUMUL-JEWME WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  16,64,WE MA ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEJKEL-KITABE ‘ILLA LITUBEJJINE LEHUMUL-LEDHI EHTELEFU FIHI WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  16,65,WEL-LAHU ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHJA BIHIL-’ERDE BA’DE MEWTIHA ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JESMA’UNE
  16,66,WE ‘INNE LEKUM FIL-’EN’AM LA’IBRETEN NUSKIKUM MIMMA FI BUTUNIHI MIN BEJNI FERTHIN WE DEMIN LEBENÆN HALISÆN SA’IGÆN LILSHSHARIBINE
  16,67,WE MIN THEMERATI EN-NEHILI WEL-’A’NABI TETTEHIDHUNE MINHU SEKERÆN WE RIZKÆN HESENÆN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  16,68,WE ‘EWHA REBBUKE ‘ILA EN-NEHLI ‘ENI ETTEHIDHI MINEL-XHIBALI BUJUTÆN WE MINE ESH-SHEXHERI WE MIMMA JA’RISHUNE
  16,69,THUMME KULI MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI FASLUKI SUBULE RABBIKI DHULULÆN JEHRUXHU MIN BUTUNIHA SHERABUN MUHTELIFUN ‘ELWANUHU FIHI SHIFA’UN LILNNASI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  16,70,WEL-LAHU HALEKAKUM THUMME JETEWEFFAKUM WE MINKUM MEN JUREDDU ‘ILA ‘ERDHELIL-’UMURI LIKEJ LA JA’LEME BA’DE ‘ILMIN SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN KADIRUN
  16,71,WEL-LAHU FEDDELE BA’DEKUM ‘ALA BA’DIN FI ER-RIZKI FEMAL-LEDHINE FUDDILU BIRADDI RIZKIHIM ‘ALA MA MELEKET ‘EJMANUHUM FEHUM FIHI SEWA’UN ‘EFEBINI’METI ELLAHI JEXHHEDUNE
  16,72,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN ‘ENFUSIKUM ‘EZWAXHÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN ‘EZWAXHIKUM BENINE WE HEFEDETEN WE REZEKAKUM MINET-TEJJIBATI ‘EFEBIALBATILI JU’UMINUNE WE BINI’METI ELLAHI HUM JEKFURUNE
  16,73,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JEMLIKU LEHUM RIZKÆN MINE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JESTETI’UNE
  16,74,FELA TEDRIBU LILLAHIL-’EMTHALE ‘INNALL-LLAHE JA’LEMU WE ‘ENTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  16,75,DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN ‘ABDÆN MEMLUKÆN LA JEKDIRU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE MEN REZEKNAHU MINNA RIZKÆN HESENÆN FEHUWE JUNFIKU MINHU SIRRÆN WE XHEHRÆN HEL JESTEWUNEL-HEMDU LILLAHI BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,76,WE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN REXHULEJNI ‘EHEDUHUMA ‘EBKEMU LA JEKDIRU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE HUWE KELLUN ‘ALA MEWLAHU ‘EJNEMA JUWEXHXHHHHU LA JE’TI BIHAJRIN HEL JESTEWI HUWE WE MEN JE’MURU BIL-’ADLI WE HUWE ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  16,77,WE LILLEHI GAJBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA ‘EMRU ES-SA’ATI ‘ILLA KELEMHIL-BESERI ‘EW HUWE ‘EKREBU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  16,78,WEL-LAHU ‘EHREXHEKUM MIN BUTUNI ‘UMMEHATIKUM LA TA’LEMUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUMU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WEL-’EF’IDETE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  16,79,‘ELEM JEREW ‘ILAT-TEJRI MUSEHHARATIN FI XHEWWI ES-SEMA’I MA JUMSIKUHUNNE ‘ILLALLAHU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  16,80,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN BUJUTIKUM SEKENÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN XHULUDIL-’EN’AMI BUJUTÆN TESTEHIFFUNEHA JEWME DHA’NIKUM WE JEWME ‘IKAMETIKUM WE MIN ‘ESWAFIHA WE ‘EWBARIHA WE ‘ESH’ARIHA ‘ETHATHÆN WE META’ÆN ‘ILA HININ
  16,81,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIMMA HALEKA DHILALÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MINEL-XHIBALI ‘EKNANÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM SERABILE TEKIKUMUL-HERRE WE SERABILE TEKIKUM BE’SEKUM KEDHALIKE JUTIMMU NI’METEHU ‘ALEJKUM LE’ALLEKUM TUSLIMUNE
  16,82,FE’IN TEWELLEW FE’INNEMA ‘ALEJKEL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  16,83,JA’RIFUNE NI’METEL-LAHI THUMME JUNKIRUNEHA WE ‘EKTHERUHUMUL-KAFIRUNE
  16,84,WE JEWME NEB’ATHU MIN KULLI ‘UMMETIN SHEHIDÆN THUMME LA JU’UDHENU LILLEDHINE KEFERU WE LA HUM JUSTA’TEBUNE
  16,85,WE ‘IDHA RE’AL-LEDHINE DHELEMUL-’ADHABE FELA JUHAFFEFU ‘ANHUM WE LA HUM JUNDHERUNE
  16,86,WE ‘IDHA RE’AL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU SHUREKA’EHUM KALU REBBENA HA’UULA’ SHUREKA’UUNAL-LEDHINE KUNNA NED’U MIN DUNIKE FE’ELKAW ‘ILEJHIMUL-KAWLE ‘INNEKUM LEKADHIBUNE
  16,87,WE ‘ELKAW ‘ILA ELLAHI JEWME’IDHIN ES-SELEME WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  16,88,EL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE SEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI ZIDNAHUM ‘ADHABÆN FEWKAL-’ADHABI BIMA KANU JUFSIDUNE
  16,89,WE JEWME NEB’ATHU FI KULLI ‘UMMETIN SHEHIDÆN ‘ALEJHIM MIN ‘ENFUSIHIM WE XHI’NA BIKE SHEHIDÆN ‘ALA HA’UULA’ WE NEZZELNA ‘ALEJKEL-KITABE TIBJANÆN LIKULLI SHEJ’IN WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN WE BUSHRA LILMUSLIMINE
  16,90,‘INNALL-LLAHE JE’MURU BIL-’ADLI WEL-’IHSANI WE ‘ITA’I DHIL-KURBA WE JENHA ‘ANIL-FEHSHA’I WEL-MUNKERI WEL-BEGJI JA’IDHUKUM LE’ALLEKUM TEDHEKKERUNE
  16,91,WE ‘EWFU BI’AHDI ELLAHI ‘IDHA ‘AHEDTUM WE LA TENKUDUL-’EJMANE BA’DE TEWKIDIHA WE KAD XHE’ALTUMU ELLAHE ‘ALEJKUM KEFILÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE JA’LEMU MA TEF’ALUNE
  16,92,WE LA TEKUNU KALLETI NEKADET GAZLEHA MIN BA’DI KUWETIN ‘ENKATHÆN TETTEHIDHUNE ‘EJMANEKUM DEHALÆN BEJNEKUM ‘EN TEKUNE ‘UMMETUN HIJE ‘ERBA MIN ‘UMMETIN ‘INNEMA JEBLUKUMU ELLAHU BIHI WE LEJUBEJJINENNE LEKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI MA KUNTUM FIHI TEHTELIFUNE
  16,93,WE LEW SHA’EL-LAHU LEXHE’ALEKUM ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN WE LEKIN JUDILLU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U WE LETUS’ELUNNE ‘AMMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  16,94,WE LA TETTEHIDHU ‘EJMANEKUM DEHALÆN BEJNEKUM FETEZILLE KADEMUN BA’DE THUBUTIHA WE TEDHUKU ES-SU’E BIMA SEDEDTUM ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE LEKUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  16,95,WE LA TESHTERU BI’AHDI ELLAHI THEMENÆN KALILÆN ‘INNEMA ‘INDEL-LAHI HUWE HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  16,96,MA ‘INDEKUM JENFEDU WE MA ‘INDEL-LAHI BAKIN WE LENEXHZIJENNEL-LEDHINE SEBERU ‘EXHREHUM BI’EHSENI MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  16,97,MEN ‘AMILE SALIHÆN MIN DHEKERIN ‘EW ‘UNTHA WE HUWE MU’UMINUN FELENUHJIJENNEHU HEJÆTEN TEJJIBETEN WE LENEXHZIJENNEHUM ‘EXHREHUM BI’EHSENI MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  16,98,FE’IDHA KARE’TEL-KUR’ANE FASTA’IDH BILLAHI MINE ESH-SHEJTANI ER-REXHIMI
  16,99,‘INNEHU LEJSE LEHU SULTANUN ‘ALEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  16,100,‘INNEMA SULTANUHU ‘ALEL-LEDHINE JETEWELLEWNEHU WEL-LEDHINE HUM BIHI MUSHRIKUNE
  16,101,WE ‘IDHA BEDDELNA ‘AJETEN MEKANE ‘AJETIN WEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA JUNEZZILU KALU ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE MUFTERIN BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,102,KUL NEZZELEHU RUHUL-KUDUSI MIN RABBIKE BIL-HEKKI LIJUTHEBBITEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE HUDEN WE BUSHRA LILMUSLIMINE
  16,103,WE LEKAD NA’LEMU ‘ENNEHUM JEKULUNE ‘INNEMA JU’ALLIMUHU BESHERUN LISANUL-LEDHI JULHIDUNE ‘ILEJHI ‘A’XHEMIJUN WE HEDHA LISANUN ‘AREBIJUN MUBINUN
  16,104,‘INNEL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI LA JEHDIHIMU ELLAHU WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  16,105,‘INNEMA JEFTERIL-KEDHIBEL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-KADHIBUNE
  16,106,MEN KEFERE BILLAHI MIN BA’DI ‘IMANIHI ‘ILLA MEN ‘UKRIHE WE KALBUHU MUTME’INNUN BIL-’IMANI WE LEKIN MEN SHEREHE BIL-KUFRI SEDRÆN FE’ALEJHIM GADEBUN MINEL-LAHI WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  16,107,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUMU ESTEHEBBUL-HEJÆTE ED-DUNJA ‘ALEL-’AHIRETI WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LA JEHDIL-KAWMEL-KAFIRINE
  16,108,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE TEBE’ALLAHU ‘ALA KULUBIHIM WE SEM’IHIM WE ‘EBSARIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-GAFILUNE
  16,109,LA XHEREME ‘ENNEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  16,110,THUMME ‘INNE REBBEKE LILLEDHINE HAXHERU MIN BA’DI MA FUTINU THUMME XHAHEDU WE SEBERU ‘INNE REBBEKE MIN BA’DIHA LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,111,JEWME TE’TI KULLU NEFSIN TUXHADILU ‘AN NEFSIHA WE TUWEFFA KULLU NEFSIN MA ‘AMILET WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  16,112,WE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN KARJETEN KANET ‘AMINETEN MUTME’INNETEN JE’TIHA RIZKUHA REGADÆN MIN KULLI MEKANIN FEKEFERET BI’EN’UMI ELLAHI FE’EDHAKAHALLAHU LIBASEL-XHU’I WEL-HAWFI BIMA KANU JESNA’UNE
  16,113,WE LEKAD XHA’EHUM RESULUN MINHUM FEKEDHDHEBUHU FE’EHADHEHUMUL-’ADHABU WE HUM DHALIMUNE
  16,114,FEKULU MIMMA REZEKAKUMU ELLAHU HELALÆN TEJJIBÆN WE ESHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘IN KUNTUM ‘IJAHU TA’BUDUNE
  16,115,‘INNEMA HERREME ‘ALEJKUMUL-MEJTETE WE ED-DEME WE LEHMEL-HINZIRI WE MA ‘UHILLE LIGAJRI ELLAHI BIHI FEMENI EDTURRE GAJRE BAGIN WE LA ‘ADIN FE’INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,116,WE LA TEKULU LIMA TESIFU ‘ELSINETUKUMUL-KEDHIBE HADHA HELALUN WE HEDHA HERAMUN LITEFTERU ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE LA JUFLIHUNE
  16,117,META’UN KALILUN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  16,118,WE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE HADU HERREMNA MA KASESNA ‘ALEJKE MIN KABLU WE MA DHELEMNAHUM WE LEKIN KANU ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  16,119,THUMME ‘INNE REBBEKE LILLEDHINE ‘AMILU ES-SU’E BIXHEHALETIN THUMME TABU MIN BA’DI DHALIKE WE ‘ESLEHU ‘INNE REBBEKE MIN BA’DIHA LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,120,‘INNE ‘IBRAHIME KANE ‘UMMETEN KANITÆN LILLAHI HENIFÆN WE LEM JEKU MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  16,121,SHAKIRÆN LI’N’UMIHI EXHTEBAHU WE HEDAHU ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIM
  16,122,WE ‘ATEJNAHU FI ED-DUNJA HESENETEN WE ‘INNEHU FIL-’AHIRETI LEMINE ES-SALIHINE
  16,123,THUMME ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE ‘ENI ETTEBI’ MILLETE ‘IBRAHIME HENIFÆN WE MA KANE MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  16,124,‘INNEMA XHU’ILE ES-SEBTU ‘ALEL-LEDHINE EHTELEFU FIHI WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEJEHKUMU BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  16,125,ED’U ‘ILA SEBILI RABBIKE BIL-HIKMETI WEL-MEW’IDHETIL-HESENETI WE XHADILHUM BI-ETI HIJE ‘EHSENU ‘INNE REBBEKE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIMEN DELLE ‘AN SEBILIHI WE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIL-MUHTEDINE
  16,126,WE ‘IN ‘AKABTUM FA’AKIBU BIMITHLI MA ‘UKIBTUM BIHI WE LE’IN SEBERTUM LEHUWE HAJRUN LILSSABIRINE
  16,127,WE ESBIR WE MA SEBRUKE ‘ILLA BILLAHI WE LA TEHZEN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA TEKU FI DEJKIN MIMMA JEMKURUNE
  16,128,‘INNALL-LLAHE ME’AL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW WEL-LEDHINE HUM MUHSINUNE